1
00:00:25,157 --> 00:00:29,924
干得好，哥们，看来早餐有冰冻寿司吃了
Well done, boys. Looks like ice-cold sushi for breakfast.

2
00:00:49,114 --> 00:00:52,106
儿子，这儿
No, no, son. Over here.

3
00:00:52,784 --> 00:00:55,514
看见这狮子吗？过来抓他
See the lion? Look at the lion and get the lion.

4
00:01:00,292 --> 00:01:02,021
儿子，如果你长大以后
Now, son, if you're gonna grow up

5
00:01:02,093 --> 00:01:05,460
像你老爹一样，你要学会如何搏斗
and be like your daddy someday, you gotta learn how to fight.

6
00:01:05,797 --> 00:01:07,128
大大
Da-da.

7
00:01:08,467 --> 00:01:11,800
阿拉凯，我给你看点东西
Now, Alakay, let me show you something, OK?

8
00:01:12,637 --> 00:01:14,298
你看见这记号了吗？
You see this mark?

9
00:01:15,140 --> 00:01:16,801
你和我是一样的
You and me are the same.

10
00:01:17,142 --> 00:01:20,373
你长大以后，你会成为狮王，像我一样
When you're bigger, you'll be Alpha Lion, just like me.

11
00:01:20,512 --> 00:01:23,208
现在让我看看你是怎么搏斗的，准备好了吗？
Now let me see you fight. Ready?

12
00:01:23,648 --> 00:01:25,980
不，阿拉凯，不准跳舞！
No, Alakay. No dancing!

13
00:01:26,485 --> 00:01:28,919
你还真自得其乐
You just amuse yourself, don't you?

14
00:01:28,987 --> 00:01:33,754
你真是个奇怪的小孩，奇怪的一个
You're a strange kid. You're a strange one. I'm...

15
00:01:33,825 --> 00:01:36,089
我们再来试一遍
Now, come on, let's try it again.

16
00:01:36,161 --> 00:01:38,061
别这样，阿拉凯
No, Alakay.

17
00:01:38,129 --> 00:01:40,597
停下来，别这样！
Stop that right now. Doggone it!

18
00:01:40,665 --> 00:01:44,101
望子成龙，却总是让人失望
It's so disappointing when they don't grow up the way you want.

19
00:01:44,169 --> 00:01:47,570
马库加，你还想挑战我？
Makunga. You're not challenging me again, are you?

20
00:01:47,639 --> 00:01:52,042
往好处想，等我击败你当了狮王
Look on the bright side. After I defeat you and become alpha lion,

21
00:01:52,110 --> 00:01:55,238
你就可以整天陪着你那可悲的儿子了
you'll have more time to spend with your pathetic son.

22
00:01:57,349 --> 00:02:00,614
在我狂扁你之前，我先问问你：
Before I kick your butt, let me ask you:

23
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:03,279
你为什么总是想当狮王？
Why do you want to become the alpha lion?

24
00:02:03,321 --> 00:02:06,620
我比你帅，发型比你美，也比你聪明…
I'm better looking, I have better hair, I'm deceivingly smart...

25
00:02:06,691 --> 00:02:09,023
…我还想让所有人对我唯命是从
...and I want everyone else to do what I say.

26
00:02:10,529 --> 00:02:13,362
数到三，我就上了，一…
We fight on three. One...

27
00:02:13,698 --> 00:02:17,532
注意，阿拉凯，看着老爸是怎么教训他的
Pay attention, Alakay. Daddy will show you how it's done.

28
00:02:17,869 --> 00:02:19,200
二，三！
Two, three!

29
00:02:41,826 --> 00:02:44,158
- 谁才是狮王？ - 是你
- Who's the alpha lion? - You are.

30
00:02:44,563 --> 00:02:46,224
你可别再忘了
Don't you forget it.

31
00:02:46,498 --> 00:02:49,399
看好了，阿拉凯，这才叫实力…
And that, Alakay, is how you attack...

32
00:02:50,735 --> 00:02:51,861
阿拉凯？
Alakay?

33
00:02:51,871 --> 00:02:54,399
（动物保护区） （禁止捕猎）

34
00:02:56,741 --> 00:03:00,734
对了，过来，小猫咪
That's it. Here, kitty, kitty.

35
00:03:01,980 --> 00:03:03,641
这个漂亮
This one's a beauty.

36
00:03:04,416 --> 00:03:05,974
能值几个钱的
He'll be worth a few bucks.

37
00:03:07,085 --> 00:03:09,246
越来越简单了
It just gets easier and easier.

38
00:03:11,256 --> 00:03:12,518
爸爸！
Daddy!

39
00:03:12,591 --> 00:03:14,582
阿拉凯！阿拉凯！
Alakay! Alakay!

40
00:03:15,093 --> 00:03:16,993
阿拉凯！
Alakay!

41
00:03:19,531 --> 00:03:21,590
大大！
Da-da!

42
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:24,091
不要啊！不要啊！
No! No! No!

43
00:03:27,205 --> 00:03:28,263
阿拉凯！
Alakay!

44
00:03:38,984 --> 00:03:42,010
- 爸爸！ - 爸爸来了！别怕！
- Daddy! - Daddy's got you! Hold on!

45
00:03:46,458 --> 00:03:48,449
大大！
Da-da!

46
00:04:03,141 --> 00:04:05,132
阿拉凯！
Alakay!

47
00:04:11,316 --> 00:04:13,648
爸爸！
Daddy!

48
00:04:34,016 --> 00:04:38,448
片名：马达加斯加2：逃往非洲

49
00:04:54,392 --> 00:04:57,520
（捕鱼捞起小狮子）
I'm a fish out of water Lion out of the jungle

50
00:05:27,392 --> 00:05:30,725
- 我不喜欢他的样子 - 他有点可爱的
- I don't like the looks of this guy. - He's kind of cute.

51
00:05:30,795 --> 00:05:32,990
他有点炫耀
He's kind of a showoff.

52
00:05:33,064 --> 00:05:35,396
你觉得他可爱？
You think he's cute?

53
00:05:47,912 --> 00:05:49,743
嗷！！
Roar!!

54
00:05:50,749 --> 00:05:53,411
纽约之王…
The King of New York City...

55
00:05:53,752 --> 00:05:56,585
…雄狮阿历克斯
...Alex the Lion!

56
00:05:57,155 --> 00:05:59,817
我还是觉得他有点炫耀
I still think he's kind of a showoff.

57
00:06:00,091 --> 00:06:01,956
他是个动物
The guy's an animal.

58
00:06:02,026 --> 00:06:06,019
也许他需要轻松一下 我们也需要度个假什么的
Maybe he should take a break. You know, we could all use a vacation.

59
00:06:06,097 --> 00:06:08,088
少来了，我们能去哪里度假？
Come on, where would we go on vacation?

60
00:06:08,366 --> 00:06:11,699
我不知道你要去哪，我可想去康涅狄格州
I don't know about you, but I want to go to Connecticut!

61
00:06:11,936 --> 00:06:15,963
包括世界闻名的雄狮阿历克斯在内的几只动物
On the loose, several animals, including the world famous Alex the Lion,

62
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:19,134
今晚从中央动物园逃脱
escaped from the Central Park Zoo tonight.

63
00:06:19,210 --> 00:06:22,441
动物们被追逃进了中央车站
The escapees were cornered in Grand Central Station.

64
00:06:22,781 --> 00:06:25,614
他是只讨厌的小猫
He was a very bad kitty.

65
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:28,646
动物保护组织曾说服动物园
Animal rights activists, who convinced zoo officials

66
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,984
将动物们送去非洲
to have the animals sent to Africa,

67
00:06:31,055 --> 00:06:34,388
他们如今惊讶的获知，运载动物们去非洲的货船
were stunned to learn that the freighter carrying the animals

68
00:06:34,459 --> 00:06:36,051
今天据悉在海上失踪
was reported missing today.

69
00:06:36,628 --> 00:06:40,223
今晚，数百纽约市民在动物园聚集
Tonight, hundreds of New Yorkers have gathered at the zoo

70
00:06:40,298 --> 00:06:42,892
哀悼他们喜爱的动物们
to mourn the loss of their beloved zoo animals.

71
00:06:42,967 --> 00:06:46,926
每个人都在想， 他们现在在哪呢？
The question on everyone's mind, where are they now?

72
00:07:36,287 --> 00:07:40,781
大家一起来，你们都会唱的，不老套的
Come on! Y'all know this one! It never gets stale!

73
00:07:42,594 --> 00:07:46,052
我们会想念你们这些小毛球的 你们真是好听众
We'll miss you little fuzz buckets! You've been a great crowd!

74
00:07:46,130 --> 00:07:48,530
很荣幸能教会你们如何用马桶
Glad we could introduce you to the toilet.

75
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:51,694
如果你们要来曼哈顿拜访，随时给我们打电话
If you ever come look us up in Manhattan, feel free to call first.

76
00:07:54,205 --> 00:07:56,366
说真的，要打电话，好不好？
Seriously though, call. OK?

77
00:07:56,708 --> 00:07:59,472
安静点，诸位
Settle down, everybody. Be quiet!

78
00:07:59,577 --> 00:08:01,568
你们不尝尝这个就走可不行
You can't leave without this!

79
00:08:01,813 --> 00:08:03,940
很惊喜吧，怪胎们！
Surprise, freaks!

80
00:08:04,716 --> 00:08:06,707
摇起来，摇起来
Shake it! Shake it.

81
00:08:07,485 --> 00:08:10,613
看，我是个美女，我是个美女，一起来
Look, I'm a lady! I'm a lady, everyone!

82
00:08:10,889 --> 00:08:15,053
我是个美女，假的啦，是我，朱利安国王
I'm a lady! Not really! It's me, King Julien!

83
00:08:15,393 --> 00:08:19,295
谁被我迷倒啦？举手
Which of you is attracted to me? Hands up!

84
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:27,394
怪胎们，你们肯定很开心， 因为我要和你们一起走
Hey, freaks! You will be very glad to hear that I am coming with you.

85
00:08:28,573 --> 00:08:30,063
哦，不用了，多谢
Oh, no, thank you.

86
00:08:30,975 --> 00:08:33,409
要的，多谢，那是我的飞机！
Yes, thank you. It's my plane!

87
00:08:33,745 --> 00:08:38,409
在我从新大陆带回纪念品之前…
Until I return with the spoils from the new country...

88
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:41,583
…史迪威是老大！
...Stevie will be in charge!

89
00:08:45,757 --> 00:08:48,419
我觉得他们不太喜欢这个主意啊
I don't think they like that idea.

90
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:50,751
你说什么，史迪威？
What are you saying, Stevie?

91
00:08:52,130 --> 00:08:53,688
不会吧
No.

92
00:08:53,765 --> 00:08:58,202
可以吗？不是吧！这怎么可能？
Could we? No, you didn't say that! How is that even possible?

93
00:08:58,269 --> 00:09:02,137
真是小淘气！史迪威说…
Naughty little thing! Stevie says...

94
00:09:02,273 --> 00:09:04,207
把蛋糕给他们吃吧！
Let them eat cake!

95
00:09:04,275 --> 00:09:07,210
朱利安国王，等等我！
King Julien, wait for me!

96
00:09:07,278 --> 00:09:10,543
我已经收拾好了！旅程也计划好了！
I'm all packed! I have a whole itinerary planned!

97
00:09:10,949 --> 00:09:13,611
啊，是莫特！烦人的家伙！
Oh, no! It's Mort! He's so annoying!

98
00:09:13,885 --> 00:09:15,853
别让他上来，抓住他！
Don't let him on. Stop that thing!

99
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:18,946
他带着剪刀和护手霜！
He's carrying scissors and hand cream!

100
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:25,953
大家都进去，快点，快进去！
Everybody in! Quickly, get in, get in! Get in quick!

101
00:09:26,164 --> 00:09:27,495
- 支架 - 检查完毕
- Struts. - Check.

102
00:09:27,665 --> 00:09:28,654
- 机翼 - 检查完毕
- Flaps. - Check.

103
00:09:28,833 --> 00:09:30,323
- 引擎，咖啡机 - 检查完毕
- Engine. Coffee maker. - Check.

104
00:09:30,802 --> 00:09:32,463
你们这些傻瓜！
You guys!

105
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,969
想都别想
Oopsie-daisy!

106
00:09:38,643 --> 00:09:41,976
这肯定是我见过的第二大的弹弓了
That has to be the second biggest slingshot I've ever seen.

107
00:09:42,313 --> 00:09:44,474
不过没办法啦，全体注意
But it'll have to do. Attention.

108
00:09:44,716 --> 00:09:46,149
我是机长
This is your captain speaking.

109
00:09:46,384 --> 00:09:49,376
一旦发生紧急情况，请穿上救生夹克
In the event of an emergency, place the vest over your head

110
00:09:49,654 --> 00:09:51,315
然后和这个世界说再见
then kiss your... good-bye.

111
00:09:51,723 --> 00:09:53,588
纽约，我们来了！
New York City, here we come!

112
00:09:53,658 --> 00:09:56,388
请向各路神仙祈祷这破烂能飞起来吧
Pray to your personal God this hunk of junk flies.

113
00:09:56,661 --> 00:09:58,595
各路神仙？破烂？说什么？
Personal God, hunk? What?

114
00:09:59,497 --> 00:10:00,987
启动了，机长
We are go, sir.

115
00:10:01,265 --> 00:10:04,166
开门！我还没进去！
Open the door! I'm outside!

116
00:10:04,502 --> 00:10:06,163
如果机舱失压
If cabin pressure is lost,

117
00:10:06,404 --> 00:10:09,931
请戴上面具，别让人看见你吓得要死
place the mask over your face to hide your terrified expression.

118
00:10:10,174 --> 00:10:14,167
对不起，小姐，这带子不该是连在座位上的吗？
Miss, aren't these supposed to be attached to my seat?

119
00:10:14,379 --> 00:10:16,677
- 不是，先生 - 好了，小伙子们，发射！
- No, sir. - OK, boys, launch!

120
00:10:18,016 --> 00:10:19,313
发射！
Launch!

121
00:10:19,384 --> 00:10:20,510
- 发射！ - 发射！
- Launch! - Launch!

122
00:11:01,726 --> 00:11:02,886
有鬼！
Gremlin!

123
00:11:06,397 --> 00:11:07,728
嗨，莫特
Hey, Mort.

124
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:09,992
嗨！
Hi!

125
00:11:14,138 --> 00:11:15,127
真奇怪
That was weird.

126
00:11:15,339 --> 00:11:18,467
- 有人还没睡醒 - 我觉得我刚才看见莫特在机翼上
- Somebody's dreaming. - I think I saw Mort on the plane wing.

127
00:11:18,743 --> 00:11:20,574
是你太想念马达加斯加了
You got Madagascar on the brain.

128
00:11:20,812 --> 00:11:22,177
我一定会想的
I know I'm gonna miss it.

129
00:11:22,246 --> 00:11:26,615
那儿是很不错，不过我觉得 我们离的越远记忆越美好
It was incredible. I think it'll seem more fun the further we are from it.

130
00:11:26,684 --> 00:11:28,345
哪种美好？就像你咬了我屁股那样？
Like when you bit me on the butt?

131
00:11:28,419 --> 00:11:32,856
我会把你念念不忘的这事用在舞台上
I'm gonna take that thing you're holding onto and use it onstage.

132
00:11:32,924 --> 00:11:36,690
算是我的沙拉吧台上的情感点心吧
It's all part of my little actor's salad bar of emotional tidbits.

133
00:11:36,928 --> 00:11:39,590
我的屁股也算是吧台上的点心吗？ （上集阿历克斯曾因饥饿咬了马蒂的屁股）
Are the butts next to the croutons?

134
00:11:41,099 --> 00:11:42,862
你不必处处讽刺我吧
You don't need to be sarcastic.

135
00:11:42,934 --> 00:11:47,371
等我们回去了，我想要参加相亲计划
When we get back, I might sign up for the breeding program.

136
00:11:47,438 --> 00:11:48,496
相亲计划？
Breeding program?

137
00:11:48,573 --> 00:11:51,701
我们已经够年纪谈婚论嫁了
We reach a point when we want to meet somebody.

138
00:11:51,776 --> 00:11:54,210
应该安定下来，发展一段感情
Settle down, have a relationship.

139
00:11:54,278 --> 00:11:55,404
看得出来
I can see that.

140
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:58,745
什么感情？约会吗？
What? Like dating?

141
00:11:58,816 --> 00:12:00,374
没错，是约会
Yeah, dating.

142
00:12:00,485 --> 00:12:02,976
和…和别人？
Other... other guys?

143
00:12:03,621 --> 00:12:06,283
什么叫“和别人”？
What do you mean, other guys?

144
00:12:09,794 --> 00:12:11,125
糟了！
Darn it!

145
00:12:11,796 --> 00:12:15,288
餐饮服务怎么拖了这么久还没来？！
What is holding up that beverage service?!

146
00:12:15,633 --> 00:12:17,464
我去看看
I'm gonna go check.

147
00:12:17,969 --> 00:12:20,995
你们继续聊吧，我得睡一会
You all keep talking. I'm gonna catch a few winks.

148
00:12:21,072 --> 00:12:22,972
真好笑！
It's so funny!

149
00:12:24,142 --> 00:12:28,010
我喜欢开怀大笑！笑起来…
I like laughing! It's such a nice experience!

150
00:12:28,079 --> 00:12:29,307
真有意思！
To laugh!

151
00:12:33,651 --> 00:12:36,142
能麻烦你回去吗？ 这里是头等舱
Do you mind going back? This is first class.

152
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:41,021
我可不是针对你，不过我们可比你高贵多了！
It's nothing personal. We're just better than you. Maurice, I'm open! Hit me!

153
00:12:41,092 --> 00:12:43,458
那是维瓦尔第吗？
- He shoots, he scores! - Is that Vivaldi?

154
00:12:43,528 --> 00:12:46,258
- 机舱奴隶 - 您有什么需要，马克维茨先生
- In-flight slave. - Can I help you, Mr. Mankiewicz?

155
00:12:46,330 --> 00:12:49,026
用银盘子把我的坚果端上来
Bring my nuts on a silver platter.

156
00:12:49,100 --> 00:12:51,227
我只是想问问 我们要的饮料好了没有
We were checking on our drink order.

157
00:12:51,502 --> 00:12:53,493
对不起，人手不够
Sorry. Been a little backed up.

158
00:12:53,838 --> 00:12:56,136
- 那我还是回去… - 你身子在哪？
- I guess I'll go back... - Where's your body?

159
00:12:56,274 --> 00:13:00,711
你真是让我不爽！能麻烦你回去吗？
You're freaking me out! Can you please go over there, please?

160
00:13:00,811 --> 00:13:03,974
难道这航班没有等级区分的吗？
What happened to the separation of the classes?

161
00:13:04,015 --> 00:13:06,848
这些所谓民主之类的东西都是一时的啦
I'm sure this democracy thing is just a fad.

162
00:13:08,019 --> 00:13:11,352
我们去吃点菠萝吧，小可爱
We'll go out for pineapple, my bobbly-headed boobily-boo.

163
00:13:11,589 --> 00:13:12,920
机长，看
Skipper, look.

164
00:13:13,524 --> 00:13:14,718
分析一下
Analysis.

165
00:13:14,792 --> 00:13:18,956
看起来这个小灯说明有什么异常 比如故障什么的
Looks like a small bulb used to indicate something unusual, like a malfunction.

166
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:21,225
我倒是觉得一闪一闪的很漂亮 还有催眠效果
I find it pretty and somewhat hypnotic.

167
00:13:21,299 --> 00:13:22,288
也对，长官
That too, sir.

168
00:13:22,366 --> 00:13:23,697
好吧，里克？
Right! Rico?

169
00:13:23,935 --> 00:13:24,924
飞行手册！
Manual!

170
00:13:27,205 --> 00:13:28,797
解决了
Problemo solved.

171
00:13:28,873 --> 00:13:31,205
- 我们可能没燃料了 - 你怎么知道的？
- We may be out of fuel. - Why do you think so?

172
00:13:31,475 --> 00:13:32,942
一号引擎不转了
We've lost engine one...

173
00:13:34,545 --> 00:13:36,706
二号引擎的火也熄了
...and engine two is no longer on fire.

174
00:13:36,948 --> 00:13:38,540
系好安全带，小伙子们
Buckle up, boys.

175
00:13:39,050 --> 00:13:41,143
别看，宝贝，情况可能变得很糟糕
Don't look, doll. This might get hairy.

176
00:13:41,385 --> 00:13:43,717
全体注意，我是机长
Attention! This is your captain.

177
00:13:43,955 --> 00:13:47,482
我一个好消息和一个坏消息要宣布 好消息是，我们马上要降落了
I have good and bad news. The good news is, we're landing immediately.

178
00:13:47,725 --> 00:13:50,717
坏消息是，我们坠机降落
The bad news is, we're crash-landing.

179
00:13:52,897 --> 00:13:56,663
你们知道坐飞机这种事是难免的啦
When it comes to air travel, we know you have no choice.

180
00:13:56,734 --> 00:13:58,725
谢谢乘坐企鹅航空
But thanks for choosing Air Penguin.

181
00:14:10,248 --> 00:14:14,582
举手，莫里斯！举起手来更好玩！
Raise your arms, Maurice! It's more fun when you raise your arms!

182
00:14:17,922 --> 00:14:19,253
我会飞哦！
I can fly!

183
00:14:19,523 --> 00:14:24,187
这次看来躲不掉了，我告诉你 你是我的真心朋友
This could be it, Marty! I want you to know you are a one-in-a-million friend!

184
00:14:24,262 --> 00:14:27,322
谢谢，哥们，你也是
Thanks, buddy! You're the best ever!

185
00:14:27,598 --> 00:14:30,965
- 那么，那事你也不介意吧？ - 什么事，随便说！
- And you won't mind when I tell you... - Tell me anything!

186
00:14:31,035 --> 00:14:32,832
我摔坏了你的iPod！
I broke your iPod!

187
00:14:32,903 --> 00:14:35,599
按键太小，我抓狂了！
The buttons were so small! It made me mad!

188
00:14:35,673 --> 00:14:37,937
- 惨绝人寰啊！ - 对不起啦！
- The horror! - I'm sorry!

189
00:14:38,209 --> 00:14:39,870
- 我要杀了你，咬屁股的混蛋！ - 真的是意外啦！
- I'll kill you, butt-biter! - It was an accident!

190
00:14:40,111 --> 00:14:41,669
- 意外啦！ - 混蛋！
- An accident! - Butt-biter!

191
00:14:41,946 --> 00:14:44,779
我爱你，格罗丽雅！我一直爱着你！
I love you, Gloria! I always have!

192
00:14:51,956 --> 00:14:56,950
就像爱沙滩和读书那样的爱
Like you love the beach. Or a good book. Or the beach.

193
00:15:08,139 --> 00:15:10,630
天啊，宝贝，你抖的像风中落叶
Goodness, doll, you're shaking like a leaf.

194
00:15:10,975 --> 00:15:12,636
里克，玩够了
Rico, you've had your fun.

195
00:15:12,910 --> 00:15:13,968
拉起来
Pull up.

196
00:15:16,580 --> 00:15:17,569
放下起落架
Gear down.

197
00:15:19,383 --> 00:15:21,715
慢慢的，温柔的触地
Gently. You just want to kiss the ground.

198
00:15:21,986 --> 00:15:24,648
如飞鸟啄食，像温柔爱抚 就像你亲你妹妹那样
Just a peck, a smooch, like you'd kiss your sister.

199
00:15:26,791 --> 00:15:27,780
我是说，温柔点！
I said, kiss it!

200
00:15:32,997 --> 00:15:35,932
现在稍稍刹下车就好了
Now just a little brake. Just a touch.

201
00:15:36,267 --> 00:15:38,667
将军
I believe that's checkmate.

202
00:15:45,843 --> 00:15:49,335
执行紧急迫降，机翼向上！拉！
Commence emergency landing procedure. Flaps up! Deploy!

203
00:16:05,563 --> 00:16:07,394
哦，我们到了
Oh, we're here.

204
00:16:08,065 --> 00:16:10,226
到底怎么回事？
What in the world?

205
00:16:11,569 --> 00:16:15,005
飞机哪去了？你们把飞机怎么了？
What happened to the plane? What did y'all do to the plane?

206
00:16:15,072 --> 00:16:17,506
没事，我还活着
I'm OK. I'm alive.

207
00:16:17,575 --> 00:16:21,602
我连小睡一会都不行 这不是肯尼迪国际机场
I can't even sleep for a minute. This is not JFK.

208
00:16:21,679 --> 00:16:23,704
科瓦斯基，伤亡报告
Kowalski, casualty report.

209
00:16:23,848 --> 00:16:25,748
只有两名乘客失踪
Two passengers unaccounted for.

210
00:16:26,016 --> 00:16:28,746
结果还不错嘛，干得好，小伙子们
That's a number I can live with. Good landing, boys.

211
00:16:29,019 --> 00:16:31,419
谁说企鹅不能飞的？
Who says a penguin can't fly?

212
00:16:31,822 --> 00:16:36,486
嗨，你们这还庆祝？看看飞机
Hey, happy slappers! Is there some reason to celebrate? Look at the plane!

213
00:16:36,761 --> 00:16:39,195
- 我们会修好的 - 你们要怎么修？
- We'll fix it. - How are you gonna fix this?

214
00:16:39,263 --> 00:16:42,096
勇气、口水还有一卷胶带
Grit, spit and a whole lot of duct tape.

215
00:16:42,433 --> 00:16:46,130
我们可以在六到九月内修好
We should be up and running in, say, six to nine months.

216
00:16:46,203 --> 00:16:49,138
- 六十九个月？！ - 不，是六到九个月
- Sixty-nine months?! - No, six to nine months.

217
00:16:49,206 --> 00:16:51,936
科瓦斯基，我们要化挫折为力量
Kowalski, I say we use this setback to our advantage.

218
00:16:52,176 --> 00:16:56,272
- 这个数字你是怎么得来的？ - 你负责重新装配
- Where'd you get that number? - I want you to reconfigure the design.

219
00:16:56,514 --> 00:16:58,038
你是怎么估计时间的？
How do you estimate that?

220
00:16:58,282 --> 00:17:01,683
你，帅哥，你和你的朋友去挖个厕所先
Pretty boy! Why don't you and your friends dig a latrine.

221
00:17:01,786 --> 00:17:04,914
等等，你评什么？
Hold on. Who made you king of the plane wreck?

222
00:17:04,955 --> 00:17:09,392
你说什么？好吧，你负责，飞机你来修
Excuse me? Fine. You can be in charge. You fix the plane.

223
00:17:09,460 --> 00:17:11,826
谁说你有资格让我负责的？
Who gives you the authority to put me in charge?

224
00:17:11,896 --> 00:17:13,955
好吧，那么，还是我负责
OK, then I'll remain in charge.

225
00:17:14,198 --> 00:17:15,893
没错，你负责吧
Yeah, you will remain in charge.

226
00:17:15,966 --> 00:17:18,628
你和你那些朋友别来妨碍我们
You and your hippie friends stay out of our hair.

227
00:17:18,702 --> 00:17:21,535
太对了，因为我决定...
Correcto-mundo. Because I decided to.

228
00:17:21,605 --> 00:17:25,473
- 很好 - 听着，这事我们没完
- Good for you. - Well, this discussion isn't over.

229
00:17:25,976 --> 00:17:27,876
高等哺乳生物，你们留下来
Higher mammals! Stay with us.

230
00:17:27,945 --> 00:17:30,971
我们可以用到你们的大脑皮层和可握拳的手
We could use your front cortexes and opposable thumbs.

231
00:17:31,315 --> 00:17:34,978
菲尔，我该先用肥皂给你洗洗手的
Phil! I should wash your hands out with soap.

232
00:17:35,319 --> 00:17:38,755
这到底…他们要怎么修好飞机？
How in the hell-o will they fix this plane?!

233
00:17:38,823 --> 00:17:41,815
勇气和口水
You know, grit and spit and spit.

234
00:17:41,892 --> 00:17:44,759
很多的勇气和口水，众志成城之类
A lot of spit and grit and stick-to-it-iveness.

235
00:17:44,829 --> 00:17:47,093
听起来没什么希望
That don't sound too promising.

236
00:17:47,164 --> 00:17:49,689
太对了，我们困在这儿了
You're right. We're stuck here.

237
00:17:49,767 --> 00:17:53,760
只要我们大家还在一起就没事
As long as we're together, we'll be OK.

238
00:17:53,838 --> 00:17:57,103
没错，不过相爱可没法送我们回家
Yeah, but love ain't gonna get us home.

239
00:17:57,174 --> 00:17:59,506
看，狮子！
Behold! The lion!

240
00:17:59,610 --> 00:18:02,204
- 大伙们 - 看够了，走吧
- People! - There is much to see. Moving on.

241
00:18:02,246 --> 00:18:04,680
等等，等等，伙计们！
Wait, wait, wait! People!

242
00:18:06,684 --> 00:18:08,515
- 他们会帮我们的 - 等等！
- They'll help us! - Wait up!

243
00:18:08,853 --> 00:18:11,344
- 伙计们！伙计们！ - 帮帮我们！
- People! Stop! - Help us!

244
00:18:12,356 --> 00:18:15,018
如果你们停下来 我就给你们签名！
If you stop, I'll autograph those!

245
00:18:15,359 --> 00:18:17,623
我认识你！
I know you!

246
00:18:17,695 --> 00:18:18,753
你
You.

247
00:18:18,829 --> 00:18:20,854
是那只讨厌的小猫
It's the bad kitty.

248
00:18:29,273 --> 00:18:30,865
喜欢这招吗！
How do you like some of that?!

249
00:18:50,394 --> 00:18:52,055
还有这招！
Come in, Tokyo!

250
00:18:58,903 --> 00:19:00,234
正中要害
Right in the batteries.

251
00:19:00,504 --> 00:19:03,166
你觉得老奶奶就不能照顾自己？
You think an old lady can't take care of herself?

252
00:19:03,574 --> 00:19:06,509
下次我就不会对你这么客气了！
Next time, I won't go so easy on you!

253
00:19:07,311 --> 00:19:08,972
谢谢，亲爱的
Thank you, dear.

254
00:19:09,246 --> 00:19:10,577
开车
Moving on!

255
00:19:12,750 --> 00:19:17,084
你疯了吗？我们需要帮助 你却骚扰老太太？
Are you out of your mind? We need help and you harass old ladies?!

256
00:19:17,321 --> 00:19:19,312
疯了？
Out of my mind?

257
00:19:19,757 --> 00:19:22,248
谁才疯了？
Who's out of my mind now?

258
00:19:22,326 --> 00:19:24,692
- 看看能不能打通 - 没问题
- See if you can get an operator. - No problem.

259
00:19:24,762 --> 00:19:28,095
说我疯了，我们要回家了
Out of my mind. We're going home.

260
00:19:39,109 --> 00:19:40,770
消息E-4
Message E-4.

261
00:19:41,011 --> 00:19:44,674
用户已漫游出信号覆盖范围
The service user has roamed outside the coverage area.

262
00:19:44,949 --> 00:19:47,281
请稍候再试
Please try again later.

263
00:19:51,956 --> 00:19:53,287
我花眼了吗？
Am I trippin'?

264
00:19:53,958 --> 00:19:56,791
这些斑马…和我一样哦
All those zebras... like me.

265
00:19:57,795 --> 00:20:00,457
- 我们在哪？ - 圣地亚哥
- Where are we? - San Diego.

266
00:20:00,798 --> 00:20:03,130
这次我有40%的把握
This time I'm 40 percent sure.

267
00:20:03,467 --> 00:20:05,799
- 我认识这里 - 我觉得是非洲
- I know this place. - I think it's Africa.

268
00:20:06,036 --> 00:20:07,025
非洲？
Africa?

269
00:20:07,304 --> 00:20:08,635
一定是啦
It's got to be.

270
00:20:08,973 --> 00:20:11,464
我们祖先的摇篮
Our ancestral crib.

271
00:20:11,709 --> 00:20:13,904
这都藏在我们的血脉里，我能感觉到！
It's in our blood. I can feel it!

272
00:20:14,144 --> 00:20:16,635
不，不仅仅是这样…
No, it's more than that. It's like...

273
00:20:16,981 --> 00:20:19,814
…像是似曾相识，好像我来过这
...deja vu, like I've been here before.

274
00:20:20,050 --> 00:20:21,642
这就叫寻根！
It's like Roots!

275
00:20:21,919 --> 00:20:23,386
不是，像是…
No, it's like...

276
00:20:23,654 --> 00:20:26,817
…似曾相识，像是我来过这里
...deja vu, like I've been here before.

277
00:20:37,167 --> 00:20:38,828
我是阿历克斯！
Me Alex!

278
00:20:39,169 --> 00:20:42,332
我和我朋友们飞来的
Me and me friends fly,

279
00:20:42,673 --> 00:20:45,665
在一个金属大鸟里飞来的
fly in great metal bird.

280
00:20:47,177 --> 00:20:49,338
然后掉了下来！
Then plummet!

281
00:20:50,347 --> 00:20:51,678
砸到地上！
Smash ground!

282
00:20:52,416 --> 00:20:54,179
嘭！
Go boom!

283
00:20:55,019 --> 00:20:58,511
然后我们相遇了
Then here we emerge.

284
00:20:58,856 --> 00:21:01,882
我们只带来快乐
We offer only happiness

285
00:21:01,959 --> 00:21:03,620
和问候
and good greetings.

286
00:21:04,361 --> 00:21:07,023
他是在演坠机吗？
Is he dancing about a plane crash?

287
00:21:07,698 --> 00:21:09,529
没错，我们…没错
Yeah. We just... yeah.

288
00:21:09,867 --> 00:21:11,528
我本来以为…对不起
I thought... Sorry.

289
00:21:11,602 --> 00:21:13,763
你们是从保护区外面来的？
You came from off the reserve?

290
00:21:14,038 --> 00:21:16,871
远得很，我们其实从中央公园动物园来的
Way off. From the Central Park Zoo, actually.

291
00:21:24,715 --> 00:21:26,205
别勉强了
Don't strain yourself.

292
00:21:26,450 --> 00:21:28,645
怎么回事？
What's going on here?

293
00:21:28,719 --> 00:21:31,483
他们说是从保护区外面来的
They say they're from off the reserve.

294
00:21:31,555 --> 00:21:34,922
不可能，从保护区外来的只有人
That's impossible. Only people come from off the reserve.

295
00:21:34,992 --> 00:21:37,153
你看起来很面熟，我认识你吗？
You look familiar. Do I know you?

296
00:21:37,227 --> 00:21:39,752
你们怎么躲过盗猎者的？
How could you survive the hunters?

297
00:21:39,830 --> 00:21:42,162
我们没见到什么偷猎者啊
We didn't see any hunters.

298
00:21:42,232 --> 00:21:44,097
- 你看什么？ - 我？没看什么啊
- What are you looking at? - Me? Nothing.

299
00:21:44,168 --> 00:21:47,331
我们的水塘养不起闲人
This watering hole doesn't need any more mouths to feed.

300
00:21:47,571 --> 00:21:49,903
你们哪来的回哪去
So skedaddle back to where you came from.

301
00:21:50,140 --> 00:21:52,335
你们这儿有什么经理负责吗？
Is there a manager we could talk to?

302
00:21:52,576 --> 00:21:55,477
我明白了，你是来挑战我的！
I see. You're here to challenge me!

303
00:21:55,746 --> 00:21:57,236
什么？我没有！
What? No! No.

304
00:21:57,481 --> 00:21:59,142
我觉得是这么回事！
That's what it looks like to me!

305
00:21:59,416 --> 00:22:00,747
祖巴，等等
Zuba! Wait.

306
00:22:01,018 --> 00:22:02,747
你没看我有正事吗…
I'm trying to take care of business...

307
00:22:02,820 --> 00:22:05,482
我知道，祖巴，你等等
Yeah, yeah, Zuba. Hold on.

308
00:22:06,156 --> 00:22:07,487
阿拉凯？
Alakay?

309
00:22:08,258 --> 00:22:09,589
是你吗？
Is that you?

310
00:22:09,827 --> 00:22:13,160
不，是阿历克斯，是“克斯” 纽约尼克斯的那个“克斯”
No, it's Alex. Lx. Like New York Knicks.

311
00:22:13,430 --> 00:22:15,523
祖巴，看！
Zuba, look!

312
00:22:15,599 --> 00:22:18,591
我生来就有，兽医也查过
I've always had that. The vet checked it out.

313
00:22:18,936 --> 00:22:20,927
其实是个很漂亮的胎记
It's kind of a beauty spot, really.

314
00:22:21,004 --> 00:22:22,699
这个记号
A mark.

315
00:22:23,607 --> 00:22:26,269
好吧，气氛好像有点奇怪
All right, this is a little weird.

316
00:22:26,844 --> 00:22:29,438
亲爱的，他回来了
Honey, he's come home.

317
00:22:29,847 --> 00:22:31,474
什么？
What?

318
00:22:31,615 --> 00:22:33,446
你终于回家了
You've come home.

319
00:22:41,792 --> 00:22:42,850
儿子
Son.

320
00:22:49,133 --> 00:22:50,122
爸爸
Dad.

321
00:22:52,302 --> 00:22:55,237
妈妈和爸爸？妈妈和爸爸！
Mom and Dad? Mom and Dad!

322
00:22:55,305 --> 00:22:58,638
妈妈和爸爸！是我的妈妈和爸爸！
Mom and Dad! It's my mom and dad!

323
00:22:59,543 --> 00:23:01,204
我有妈妈和爸爸了！
I got a mom and dad!

324
00:23:01,478 --> 00:23:02,809
我孩子还活着！
My baby's alive!

325
00:23:03,080 --> 00:23:04,411
爸爸！
Dad!

326
00:23:04,648 --> 00:23:06,309
我的孩子！
My son!

327
00:23:06,984 --> 00:23:09,646
我儿子回来了！
My son is home!

328
00:23:11,555 --> 00:23:14,649
阿拉凯！阿拉凯回来了！
Alakay! Alakay has come home!

329
00:23:18,495 --> 00:23:23,159
阿拉凯！耶！走失的儿子回来了！太好了！
Alakay! Yeah! The prodigal son returns. This is perfect!

330
00:23:23,567 --> 00:23:25,660
我以为你讨厌祖巴的
I thought you hated Zuba.

331
00:23:26,170 --> 00:23:30,436
对，我是讨厌他，没错，我讨厌他
No, I do. I do. I do. I hate him. Oh, I do.

332
00:23:30,507 --> 00:23:33,032
我要利用阿拉凯，没错
And I'm going to use Alakay, yes.

333
00:23:33,110 --> 00:23:36,671
我要利用他来一劳永逸的除掉祖巴
I'm going to use him to get rid of Zuba once and for all!

334
00:23:36,914 --> 00:23:38,506
快点，长羽毛的马！
Giddy-up, feathered horse!

335
00:23:38,582 --> 00:23:41,449
让开，让开路，躲开！
Make way! Move out of the way! Stand aside!

336
00:23:41,518 --> 00:23:43,179
纽约！
New York!

337
00:23:43,520 --> 00:23:47,456
有点像垃圾场，你确实这儿不是新泽西吗？
It's a bit of a dump. Are you sure we're not in New Jersey?

338
00:23:47,524 --> 00:23:50,789
嗨，纽约众！你们的国王来了！
Hello, New Yorkers! Your new king is here!

339
00:23:50,861 --> 00:23:53,125
已经举行欢迎仪式了？
This calls for a celebration!

340
00:23:53,197 --> 00:23:55,062
莫里斯，我觉得他们喜欢我
Maurice, I think they like me.

341
