Yeah.

511
00:34:47,050 --> 00:34:50,508
我们在钢筋水泥的丛林里都生存下来了！
We survive the concrete jungle!

512
00:34:50,587 --> 00:34:54,023
需要食物时，我们去找热狗摊
When we need food, we hunt for a decent hot dog stand.

513
00:34:54,090 --> 00:34:55,751
- 是不是？ - 她说得对
- Am I right? - She's right.

514
00:34:55,825 --> 00:34:59,261
需要地方住的时候，我们建起了摩天大楼
When we need shelter, we build skyscrapers.

515
00:34:59,362 --> 00:35:03,822
- 说的太好了 - 需要水的时候，我们建起了大坝
- Exactly! - When we need water, we build a dam.

516
00:35:03,867 --> 00:35:06,062
我们是纽约人，我们自豪的高呼！
We're New Yorkers, for crying out loud!

517
00:35:06,135 --> 00:35:08,535
我们在纽约能做到的事
If we can make it there,

518
00:35:08,605 --> 00:35:11,130
我们在任何地方都能做到
we can make it anywhere!

519
00:35:27,323 --> 00:35:29,484
我来了，朱利安国王
I'm coming, King Julien!

520
00:35:35,999 --> 00:35:38,331
大坏鱼！大坏鱼！
Bad fishy! Bad fishy!

521
00:35:40,003 --> 00:35:42,335
不对，是鲨鱼啊！糟了糟了！
No, shark, no! Sit!

522
00:35:44,674 --> 00:35:46,505
我为什么要笑呢？
Why am I laughing?

523
00:35:50,079 --> 00:35:54,448
我们凑齐了全部配件，不过进度有点拖延
We have all the parts we need, but we're slightly behind schedule.

524
00:35:54,517 --> 00:35:56,883
- 拖延程度如何？ - 六到九年
- How slightly? - Six to nine years.

525
00:35:56,953 --> 00:36:00,184
- 六十九年？ - 不是，是六到九年
- Sixty-nine years? - No, six to nine years.

526
00:36:00,623 --> 00:36:02,989
小兵，我们的猴子呢？
Private! What happened to our thumbs?

527
00:36:03,059 --> 00:36:05,118
他们昨天开始就失踪了
Haven't seen them since yesterday.

528
00:36:05,194 --> 00:36:07,025
该死
Darn you, Darwin!

529
00:36:07,096 --> 00:36:12,033
竟敢在我眼皮底下溜号，小兵，你跟我来
Nobody goes AWOL on my watch. Private! You're coming with me.

530
00:36:12,702 --> 00:36:15,034
里克，你跟我来！
Rico! You're coming with me!

531
00:36:15,705 --> 00:36:19,698
- 我要送他们上军事法庭 - 不必了！
- We'll bring them in for court martial. - That won't be necessary!

532
00:36:19,776 --> 00:36:23,371
我们帮你们招募了些兄弟，机长
We've recruited a few extra thumbs for you, Skipper.

533
00:36:29,886 --> 00:36:31,717
太好了，我成猴子军长了
Well, I'll be a monkey's uncle.

534
00:36:32,055 --> 00:36:33,886
我可不觉得
Oh, I doubt that.

535
00:36:40,396 --> 00:36:42,557
别浪费时间了，我们开始工作吧
Enough lollygagging. Let's get to work.

536
00:36:42,799 --> 00:36:46,667
你们分成三组，第一组负责制作机体
There'll be three groups. Group Alpha will do sheet metal fabrication.

537
00:36:46,803 --> 00:36:50,967
第二组负责装配，第三组负责后勤
Group Bronson handles assembly. Group George Peppard, craft services.

538
00:36:51,040 --> 00:36:52,405
有什么问题？
Any questions?

539
00:36:52,742 --> 00:36:55,233
没有太好了，开始工作吧！
Good! Let's get to work.

540
00:37:02,585 --> 00:37:05,418
我真想亲你一口，猴子
I'd like to kiss you, monkey man.

541
00:37:05,755 --> 00:37:09,247
勉为其难吧，虽然你长得丑
All right, but you're so darn ugly.

542
00:37:15,431 --> 00:37:19,834
记住，小家伙们 真正的舞者是用心来表演的
Remember, little cub scouts, a great dance performance comes from the heart.

543
00:37:20,770 --> 00:37:23,261
只要用心，你就战无不胜
Straight from the heart, you'll never go wrong.

544
00:37:25,108 --> 00:37:26,200
随便你，先生
Sure, mister.

545
00:37:26,275 --> 00:37:30,302
嗨，阿拉凯，我刚好路过，过来给你鼓鼓劲
Hey, Alakay, I just happened to walk by, I thought I'd wish you luck.

546
00:37:30,380 --> 00:37:33,872
- 你不会紧张吧？有吗？ - 哪有，我靠这吃饭的
- You're not nervous, are you? - Nah, it's my thing.

547
00:37:33,950 --> 00:37:37,716
在我看来，胜利的关键在于选择对手
In my opinion, the key to this is choosing the right competitor.

548
00:37:37,787 --> 00:37:41,052
所以这是PK赛制吗？
You mean, this is like a dance battle sort of thing?

549
00:37:41,124 --> 00:37:43,183
- PK淘汰赛？ - 对吧
- Like a dance-off? - Sure.

550
00:37:43,459 --> 00:37:45,620
太好了，我喜欢自由发挥
Great. I love that. Freestyle.

551
00:37:45,962 --> 00:37:49,796
谁够格跟我比？好让比赛精彩点
Who'd be a good match for me? Just to keep things interesting.

552
00:37:50,633 --> 00:37:52,794
这我可帮不上忙
Well, I wish I could help,

553
00:37:53,069 --> 00:37:56,630
因为祖宗法纪不允许我多嘴
but that's strictly against our ancient tradition and all we hold sacred.

554
00:37:56,873 --> 00:38:00,400
不过如果是我的话，我肯定选提西
But if it was me out there... I'd choose Teetsi.

555
00:38:01,144 --> 00:38:04,580
提西，好吧，听起来蛮有趣的
Teetsi. OK. Sounds interesting.

556
00:38:04,647 --> 00:38:06,137
马库加，对吧？多谢
Makunga, right? Thank you.

557
00:38:06,416 --> 00:38:08,884
你是祖巴的孩子嘛，随时效劳，上去露一手吧
Anything for Zuba's boy. Go get 'em, tiger.

558
00:38:09,152 --> 00:38:10,483
振作精神
Shake it out.

559
00:38:11,154 --> 00:38:12,985
五六七八
A five, six, seven, eight.

560
00:38:13,322 --> 00:38:15,654
我们上，开始了
Let's go, let's do this.

561
00:38:34,010 --> 00:38:36,501
成年仪式，现在开始
Let us begin the rite of passage ceremony.

562
00:38:36,579 --> 00:38:39,912
- 加油啊，宝贝！让妈妈骄傲一下！ - 别这样，我正要主持…
- Come on, baby! Make Mama proud! - Woman, I'm trying to take...

563
00:38:39,982 --> 00:38:41,176
没问题，妈妈！
On it, Mom!

564
00:38:41,250 --> 00:38:43,013
谁想第一个上场？
Who will be the first participant?

565
00:38:43,086 --> 00:38:45,680
我，哦，让我上，让我上！
Me! Oh! Me, me, me! Me! Me! Me! Me, me! Please, me?

566
00:38:46,022 --> 00:38:48,354
就你吧，又高又帅的这位
How about you? The tall, handsome one.

567
00:38:48,591 --> 00:38:50,354
选择你的对手吧
Yeah. Choose your opponent.

568
00:38:51,027 --> 00:38:52,688
让我想想
Let me see.

569
00:38:53,863 --> 00:38:56,354
我要挑…
I guess I'll pick...

570
00:38:59,469 --> 00:39:00,458
…提西？
...Teetsi?

571
00:39:02,472 --> 00:39:04,940
提西？他为什么挑提西？
Teetsi? Why did he pick Teetsi?

572
00:39:05,208 --> 00:39:08,541
这才是我儿子，勇敢无畏！
That's my boy! He's got some gumption there!

573
00:39:09,378 --> 00:39:11,209
来人，把他叫醒！
Somebody, wake him up!

574
00:39:24,827 --> 00:39:27,660
好吧，提西，来吧，我们比试一下
All right, so, Teetsi, come on. Let's do this, huh?

575
00:39:27,730 --> 00:39:32,224
来吧，小提西，让我看看你的实力
Come on, little tsetse fly. Let's see your stuff. Bring it.

576
00:39:32,502 --> 00:39:34,470
- 开始吧！ - 好啊
- Let's dance! - OK.

577
00:39:34,537 --> 00:39:37,301
不过我警告你…
But let me warn you that I am a protege of...

578
00:39:37,573 --> 00:39:40,235
…我可是霍西和罗宾斯的得意门生
...Fosse and Robbins!

579
00:39:40,576 --> 00:39:43,067
不是跳舞，是决斗！
Not "dance" dance! Fight!

580
00:39:43,913 --> 00:39:46,245
是斗舞吗？没问题啊
Dance fight! You got it.

581
00:39:52,989 --> 00:39:54,854
- 他是在跳舞吗？ - 他到底在干嘛？
- Is he dancing? - What's he doing?

582
00:39:54,924 --> 00:39:57,256
他不可能是在跳舞吧
I know that boy is not dancing.

583
00:39:57,927 --> 00:40:00,088
比我想象中顺利多了
This is even better than I thought.

584
00:40:02,932 --> 00:40:04,422
阿拉凯，转身
Alakay, turn around!

585
00:40:04,667 --> 00:40:08,865
不，老爸，应该是： 小跳、摆头、摇臀然后才是转身
No, Pop, it's hop, shuffle, ball change, hip swish, turn around.

586
00:40:18,614 --> 00:40:20,275
哦，不会吧
Oh, no.

587
00:40:21,450 --> 00:40:23,611
阿拉凯，你受伤了吗？
Alakay! Are you hurt?

588
00:40:23,953 --> 00:40:25,614
是的，我受伤了
Yeah, I am.

589
00:40:25,888 --> 00:40:27,685
我赢了吗？
Did I... did I win?

590
00:40:27,757 --> 00:40:29,088
当然没有，儿子
No, son.

591
00:40:29,158 --> 00:40:31,217
怎么会这样？
How could this happen?

592
00:40:31,294 --> 00:40:35,355
你告诉我说你是一方之王 大王可不会打输
You told us you were a king. A king does not get beat.

593
00:40:35,431 --> 00:40:39,458
我是大王，我是纽约之王
I am a king. I'm the King of New York.

594
00:40:39,969 --> 00:40:43,928
那是我的艺名，我上台表演的时候用的
It's my stage name. Like for when I perform.

595
00:40:44,006 --> 00:40:45,166
表演？
Perform?

596
00:40:45,241 --> 00:40:49,575
太不幸了，阿拉凯没通过测试
Oh, no, this is horrible! Alakay has failed the test!

597
00:40:50,146 --> 00:40:54,810
谁能想象，今天祖巴居然要流放…
Who would have ever imagined that today Zuba would have to banish...

598
00:40:55,484 --> 00:40:57,076
…自己的亲儿子？
...his own son?

599
00:40:57,153 --> 00:40:59,212
-祖巴，不要
Zuba, no.

600
00:40:59,322 --> 00:41:01,187
祖巴，要的
Zuba, yes.

601
00:41:01,490 --> 00:41:05,324
很不幸，狮王必须要驱逐不合格的成员
Sadly, the alpha lion must cast out all failures.

602
00:41:18,007 --> 00:41:20,407
那么，我不当这个狮王了
Then I'm no longer the alpha lion.

603
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:23,171
爸爸，你干什么？
Dad, what are you doing?

604
00:41:23,512 --> 00:41:26,345
爸爸，不要！你别这样
Dad, no! You can't do this.

605
00:41:28,618 --> 00:41:31,086
谁能来接替祖巴的位置？
Who could possibly take Zuba's place?

606
00:41:32,188 --> 00:41:33,348
谁来？
Anyone?

607
00:41:33,689 --> 00:41:35,520
有人吗？没人？
Someone? No one?

608
00:41:36,425 --> 00:41:37,949
你吗？
You, sir!

609
00:41:38,027 --> 00:41:39,619
恐怕不是
I guess not.

610
00:41:39,695 --> 00:41:42,687
虽然这样很不好意思
Well, I... this is all very awkward,

611
00:41:43,032 --> 00:41:46,524
不过这个重担还是我来担吧
but I suppose I could carry this tremendous burden.

612
00:41:48,204 --> 00:41:50,536
提西，把帽子拿来
Teetsi! Get the hat.

613
00:41:52,208 --> 00:41:56,042
作为新的领袖，我宣布流放阿拉凯！
As your new leader, I hereby banish Alakay!

614
00:41:56,379 --> 00:41:58,370
并且他要戴着耻辱之帽…
He shall wear this Hat of Shame...

615
00:41:58,648 --> 00:42:01,378
…离开水源
...and leave the watering hole

616
00:42:01,717 --> 00:42:04,208
期限为一千年，或者一辈子
for a thousand years, or life!

617
00:42:05,554 --> 00:42:07,215
那个长适用哪个
Whichever comes last.

618
00:42:10,126 --> 00:42:13,061
过去，过去，走开！
Shoo, shoo! Get out of here!

619
00:42:13,396 --> 00:42:17,560
你应该先告诉我们 你不是真正的大王，儿子
You should have told us you weren't a real king, son!

620
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:20,200
你也没先告诉我要决斗啊！
You never told me I'd have to fight anybody!

621
00:42:20,269 --> 00:42:21,566
你以为呢？
What did you expect?!

622
00:42:21,637 --> 00:42:26,199
我不知道，也许你该说明白的 “儿子，那可是决斗哦！”
I don't know! Maybe a little fatherly advice like, "Hey, son, it's a fight!"

623
00:42:26,275 --> 00:42:29,073
- 你不是狮子吗？ - 但是我这辈子都没打过架
- You're a lion! - But I never fought another lion!

624
00:42:29,145 --> 00:42:31,045
你当然没有啦，你忙着跳舞呢
No, I guess not. You dance!

625
00:42:31,113 --> 00:42:35,174
当然还干别的事，问题是那个马库加给我下了套
And other stuff! Your pal, Makunga, set me up back there!

626
00:42:35,251 --> 00:42:38,015
- 这些都不会发生，如果… - 如果你是只真正的雄狮
- None of this would have happened... - If you were a real lion.

627
00:42:38,087 --> 00:42:39,816
- 祖巴！ - 是啊，我就这么说了！
- Zuba! - Yeah, I said it!

628
00:42:41,590 --> 00:42:43,251
真正的雄狮
A real lion.

629
00:42:44,260 --> 00:42:45,591
多谢
Thanks.

630
00:42:48,931 --> 00:42:50,421
真是多谢你
Thanks a lot.

631
00:43:00,376 --> 00:43:01,604
锯子
Saw.

632
00:43:02,945 --> 00:43:04,276
缝合线
Suture.

633
00:43:06,115 --> 00:43:07,446
擦汗
Swab.

634
00:43:07,717 --> 00:43:09,048
你挡住光线了，史蒂文
You're in my light, Stephen.

635
00:43:09,285 --> 00:43:11,947
你肩膀上有个褐色斑点
You have a brown spot on your shoulder.

636
00:43:12,188 --> 00:43:16,716
你观察真仔细啊，不过你看的再仔细一点 你会发现我全身都是斑点
That's very observant, Stephen. As you can see, I'm covered in brown spots.

637
00:43:16,959 --> 00:43:20,451
过几周，骨头就都长好了
OK! That bone will be good as new in a few weeks.

638
00:43:20,730 --> 00:43:22,857
那么我不用去等死了？
So I don't have to pick out a dying hole?

639
00:43:23,065 --> 00:43:25,397
当然不用，蒂姆，你的人生才刚刚开始
No, you got your whole life ahead of you.

640
00:43:25,468 --> 00:43:27,902
- 真的吗？ - 去玩吧
- Really? - Go out and grab it by the horns.

641
00:43:27,970 --> 00:43:31,633
- 谢谢你，马克维茨医生！ - 使劲玩吧，真可爱
- Thank you, Dr. Mankiewicz! - Break a leg! Sweet kid.

642
00:43:31,874 --> 00:43:34,741
那个斑点有点像巫医病的症状啊
This spot looks like Witch Doctor's Disease.

643
00:43:35,311 --> 00:43:40,146
什么巫医病？从没听说过有这么搞笑的病
Witch Doctor's Disease? That's the most ridiculous disease I've ever heard of.

644
00:43:40,983 --> 00:43:43,315
- 别问了 - 有人又淘气了
- Don't ask. - Someone's been knotty.

645
00:43:45,087 --> 00:43:46,076
放心，一点都不疼
This won't hurt a bit.

646
00:43:46,322 --> 00:43:50,588
我们上一个巫医乔，也得了这种病
Joe, our last witch doctor, had a spotjust like that.

647
00:43:50,659 --> 00:43:54,823
- 然后呢？ - 星期一还在，星期三就挂了
- And? - Monday, Joe. Wednesday, no Joe.

648
00:43:55,564 --> 00:43:56,895
三天就挂了？
Wednesday, no Joe?

649
00:43:57,099 --> 00:43:59,431
终于可以呼吸了，谢了，医生
I can breathe! Thanks, doc!

650
00:43:59,668 --> 00:44:03,570
这巫医病居然是真的？
So this Witch Doctor's Disease is a real thing?

651
00:44:03,906 --> 00:44:07,433
你会想出办法的，你至少还有48小时能活哪嘛
You'll find a cure. You've got at least 48 hours!

652
00:44:07,510 --> 00:44:09,603
但是我从来没听说过这病啊
But I've never heard of it.

653
00:44:09,678 --> 00:44:12,943
这儿连青霉素都没有
I mean... I dont have any penicillin.

654
00:44:13,015 --> 00:44:15,449
我怎么都得先照个X光看看怎么回事吧
I'll need a CAT scan just to get started!

655
00:44:15,518 --> 00:44:18,851
找个狮子帮忙看看里面怎么回事吧 他们肯定乐意的
Have a lion look you over. They'd be happy to.

656
00:44:29,565 --> 00:44:30,554
噔噔！
Ta-da!!

657
00:44:30,866 --> 00:44:33,460
- 他真厉害啊 - 真是酷毙啦
- He has talent. - Stupendous and tremendous.

658
00:44:35,137 --> 00:44:39,301
这招你们肯定没见过吧，把纽约人都迷翻了
Bet you've never seen that one! Knocked 'em dead in New York!

659
00:44:39,375 --> 00:44:41,366
- 大家试试看吧！ - 好啊好啊！
- Let's all give it a try! - Let's do it!

660
00:44:41,710 --> 00:44:44,110
你们可以尽管试
Well, you can try all you want to,

661
00:44:44,180 --> 00:44:46,205
不过这可是我多年苦练的成果
but it takes years of practice.

662
00:44:46,282 --> 00:44:48,307
你得先锻炼你的嘴部肌肉到丰满有力
You'll never get a tight stream

663
00:44:48,384 --> 00:44:52,844
然后你才可以把嘴巴撅成这样喷水
until you build up your lip muscles to the point where you can

664
00:44:52,922 --> 00:44:55,083
明白了吗？
purse your lips like this. You got it?

665
00:45:08,904 --> 00:45:10,064
噔噔！
Ta-da!

666
00:45:13,909 --> 00:45:17,140
你们怎么会的？简直一模一样！
How did you? You guys got it right out of the box!

667
00:45:17,213 --> 00:45:19,010
- 你会的 - 我们都会
- If you can do it... ...we can do it.

668
00:45:19,081 --> 00:45:20,309
流淌在我们的血液里
It's in our blood!

669
00:45:20,583 --> 00:45:23,313
我还以为我很特别呢
I always thought I was a bit unique.

670
00:45:23,385 --> 00:45:24,579
我们都很特别
We are unique!

671
00:45:24,854 --> 00:45:26,651
号称自然原力的就是我们啦
We are like a force of nature!

672
00:45:26,922 --> 00:45:29,584
- 光芒万点 - 还有黑色条纹
- A million points of light! - And dark stripes!

673
00:45:29,658 --> 00:45:31,853
一模一样！
Exactly the same!

674
00:45:32,761 --> 00:45:35,252
一模一样
Exactly the same.

675
00:45:36,665 --> 00:45:40,260
看起来很不错，科瓦斯基 不过这东西能飞起来吗？
Looks impressive, Kowalski, but will it fly?

676
00:45:40,603 --> 00:45:44,095
当然，这里折一下，还有这里那里
Yes. If we fold it here, here and here.

677
00:45:46,275 --> 00:45:47,264
很好
Nice.

678
00:45:59,788 --> 00:46:03,781
伙计们，我爸爸觉得我是个正废材
Oh, man. My dad thinks I'm a total loser.

679
00:46:04,026 --> 00:46:05,789
我毁了我父母的生活
I've ruined my parents' lives.

680
00:46:06,028 --> 00:46:07,962
这可太不酷啦
That is definitely not crack-a-lackin'.

681
00:46:08,030 --> 00:46:12,694
简直太衰了，我得弥补错误
It is lackin' in the crackin', my friend. I've gotta fix this.

682
00:46:12,968 --> 00:46:14,128
有些话
So...

683
00:46:15,137 --> 00:46:18,629
我想要跟你们说
...there's... There's something I gotta tell you.

684
00:46:18,807 --> 00:46:19,796
嗨，伙计们
Hey, guys.

685
00:46:20,809 --> 00:46:22,709
你们又没觉得，这地方真是太赞了？！
Is this place great or what?!

686
00:46:23,045 --> 00:46:24,740
我选“没觉得”
I'd go with "or what."

687
00:46:24,813 --> 00:46:28,476
听我说，你们肯定不相信，不过…
Well, I'll tell you what. You're not gonna believe it, but...

688
00:46:28,984 --> 00:46:31,475
…我跟摩托摩托约会了
...I got a date with Moto Moto.

689
00:46:32,321 --> 00:46:33,811
谁是摩托摩托？
Who's Moto Moto?

690
00:46:33,889 --> 00:46:37,484
天啊，他又壮又帅又壮！
Oh, he's so big and handsome and big!

691
00:46:37,826 --> 00:46:40,158
- 你知道摩托摩托什么意思吗？ - 双胞胎？
- Know what "Moto Moto" means? - Twins?

692
00:46:40,396 --> 00:46:42,159
意思是“超帅超帅”
It means, "Hot Hot."

693
00:46:42,364 --> 00:46:43,456
“超帅超帅”？
"Hot Hot"?

694
00:46:43,666 --> 00:46:46,328
好啊，你什么时候变成非洲通的？
When did you start parlez-ing African?

695
00:46:46,602 --> 00:46:47,591
流淌在我的血液里啦
It's in my blood.

696
00:46:47,836 --> 00:46:51,465
别担心，我死了以后 你就可以尽情和帅哥眉来眼去了
Don't worry, you can flirt around with Mr. Hot Pants after I'm gone.

697
00:46:51,540 --> 00:46:54,407
你有什么毛病，梅尔曼 干嘛在我兴头上泼冷水？
Melman, why am I the parade and you're the rain?

698
00:46:54,476 --> 00:46:56,637
我泼冷水的时候，你干嘛要在兴头上？
Why are you driving your parade under my rain?

699
00:46:56,712 --> 00:46:59,408
我的兴头又没在你家门口！
Maybe I'll parade in another part of town!

700
00:46:59,515 --> 00:47:00,880
别这样，伙计们
Whoa, guys.

701
00:47:01,083 --> 00:47:02,573
没在我家门口就好！
Main Street's mine!

702
00:47:02,651 --> 00:47:04,812
谁稀罕你家门口！
Well, you can have it!

703
00:47:04,887 --> 00:47:09,017
你可以和你的超帅先生去…
And you can take your hotee-tot float and Mr. Hotee Moto Moto...

704
00:47:09,291 --> 00:47:11,282
- 你说什么？ - 我们都在说什么呢？
- What are you talking about? - What are we talking about?

705
00:47:11,527 --> 00:47:12,858
梅尔曼，你就告诉她吧
Melman, just tell her.

706
00:47:13,195 --> 00:47:16,858
要告诉你告诉！什么…告诉她什么？ 你说什么？我听不懂
What? What are you... I don't know what you're talking about.

707
00:47:17,099 --> 00:47:18,498
那我走好了
I guess I'll go, then.

708
00:47:18,567 --> 00:47:19,966
随便你
Don't bother.

709
00:47:20,035 --> 00:47:23,630
- 你少找我麻烦 - 梅尔曼！格罗丽雅！
- Don't get up on my account. - Melman! Gloria!

710
00:47:23,706 --> 00:47:28,040
- 你们不是朋友吗！ - 马蒂说的一点没错
- I thought you guys were friends! - Marty's absolutely right.

711
00:47:28,110 --> 00:47:29,873
- 马蒂？ - 马蒂？
- Marty? - Marty?

712
00:47:30,045 --> 00:47:31,103
马蒂？
Marty?

713
00:47:32,047 --> 00:47:33,708
这到底怎么回事？
What the heck is going on?

714
00:47:33,983 --> 00:47:38,977
你不是？他是…？我觉得他是……你是？
You're not? Oh! He was... I thought he... You're not him. He's... Oh.

715
00:47:39,054 --> 00:47:41,818
你把那家伙…
You thought that guy...

716
00:47:41,890 --> 00:47:43,152
…当成我了？
...was me?

717
00:47:43,225 --> 00:47:45,989
不是，哦，是，你们…
No. I mean, yes, you... Guys, come on.

718
00:47:46,061 --> 00:47:48,222
你把我当成他了？
You thought I was him?

719
00:47:48,564 --> 00:47:50,555
你们确实长得很…
You guys kind of do look a little...

720
00:47:50,633 --> 00:47:53,295
很像啊，的确很像嘛
You look a lot alike. Marty, you look a lot alike.

721
00:47:53,369 --> 00:47:57,237
声音一样，笑声一样，连说话方式都一样
You laugh alike. Talk alike. He has the same speech pattern.

722
00:47:57,306 --> 00:48:00,366
很奇怪啦，真的，马蒂
It's a little weird, really. I mean, come on. Marty.

723
00:48:00,476 --> 00:48:03,604
所以你是说我其实一点都不特别？
So you're saying there's nothing unique about me.

724
00:48:03,812 --> 00:48:05,905
我和其他斑马没两样？
I'm just like any other zebra.

725
00:48:05,981 --> 00:48:07,573
当然不是，你一定很特别嘛！
No. Of course you're different!

726
00:48:07,916 --> 00:48:09,247
哪儿特别？
How?

727
00:48:10,919 --> 00:48:13,080
好吧，我分不出
OK, I can't tell you apart.

728
00:48:13,422 --> 00:48:16,220
也许你可以考虑带个铃铛什么的
Maybe you could wear a bell or something.

729
00:48:16,292 --> 00:48:18,920
- 铃铛？ - 好吧，这是个馊主意
- A bell?! - OK, not a bell. Bell's a bad idea.

730
00:48:19,261 --> 00:48:21,923
那我不如穿件T恤 上面写上“我旁边有个笨蛋”？
How about a T-shirt that says, "I'm with stupid"?

731
00:48:22,164 --> 00:48:24,689
- 我不是笨蛋！ - 不是说你！笨蛋！他才是笨蛋！
- I'm not stupid! - Not you, stupid! Him, stupid!

732
00:48:24,933 --> 00:48:28,266
你知道嘛，你和马群打成一片的时候
You know, while you've been doing the prancing pony with your new posse,

733
00:48:28,504 --> 00:48:31,769
我过着这辈子最倒霉的日子
I've been having the worst day of my life.

734
00:48:33,108 --> 00:48:35,440
你总是这么自我中心，是不是？
It's always about you, isn't it?

735
00:48:35,778 --> 00:48:39,043
我的麻烦比你的麻烦麻烦多了
My problems are just a little bit bigger than yours.

736
00:48:39,114 --> 00:48:41,947
我是分不清你们俩，那又怎么样？
I couldn't tell you apart. So what?!

737
00:48:42,618 --> 00:48:45,280
太好了，你就走吧，走吧
Yeah, fine. Run away, Marty! Run away!

738
00:48:45,521 --> 00:48:48,615
这你最拿手了，和在纽约时一样！
That's what you do best! Just like back in New York!

739
00:48:48,857 --> 00:48:52,122
我在这儿，不过反正你分不出来，是不是？
I'm right here. But you can't tell that, right?

740
00:48:54,396 --> 00:48:57,661
你的“真心朋友”希望你一个人
Your one-of-a-million friend hopes you enjoy

741
00:48:57,733 --> 00:49:00,566
好好享受你那“比别人麻烦的多的麻烦”！
your bigger-than-anyone-else's problems alone!

742
00:49:00,669 --> 00:49:04,264
好啊，走吧，我才不需要你帮我解决问题！
Good, leave! I don't need you to help me solve my problems!

743
00:49:04,306 --> 00:49:07,469
你们千篇一律，我才认不出谁是马蒂！
You're a dime a dozen! I can't tell which one's Marty!

744
00:49:07,543 --> 00:49:10,569
谁是马蒂？等一等，对了，我不在乎！
Which one's Marty? Wait a minute. Oh, yeah, I don't care!

745
00:49:10,646 --> 00:49:13,308
帽子好看啊，你这炫耀鬼！
Nice hat, you showoff!

746
00:49:18,821 --> 00:49:20,152
马蒂…
Marty...

747
00:49:21,156 --> 00:49:22,646
…别走
...don't go.

748
00:49:22,991 --> 00:49:23,359
跟上！跟上！
Giddy-up, giddy-up!
Giddy-up, giddy-up!

749
00:49:23,359 --> 00:49:24,656
跟上，跟上！

750
00:49:27,663 --> 00:49:28,994
看，玛瑞斯！
Look, Maurice!

751
00:49:29,231 --> 00:49:31,563
这里建造我的行宫真是再好不过了！
The perfect spot for my summer palace!

752
00:49:31,834 --> 00:49:35,668
找人把这些坑填起来，废料都搬走
Please fill in all these holes and relocate the riff-raff.

753
00:49:36,772 --> 00:49:40,003
- 这个头是谁丢的？ - 真浪费
- Who'd leave a perfectly good head? - What a waste.

754
00:49:40,342 --> 00:49:43,334
还用你说，我在等死
Tell me about it. I'm in my prime here.

755
00:49:43,679 --> 00:49:45,909
病入膏肓了，知道吗？
I'm terminal, you know?

756
00:49:46,915 --> 00:49:50,442
可能只有一两天好活了
I probably only have another two days left to live.

757
00:49:50,686 --> 00:49:52,847
原来是个流浪汉
That's a bummer, man.

758
00:49:53,188 --> 00:49:55,850
如果朱利安国王，这是我的名字…
If I, King Julien... that's my name...

759
00:49:56,191 --> 00:49:58,352
只有还能活两天
...only had two days left to live,

760
00:49:58,694 --> 00:50:00,127
我会把我想做的事情
I would do all the things

761
00:50:00,195 --> 00:50:02,686
- 统统尝试下 - 哪些事情？
- I've ever dreamed of doing. - Like what?

762
00:50:02,765 --> 00:50:05,791
我要成为一个口哨高手
I'd love to become a professional whistler.

763
00:50:05,868 --> 00:50:10,134
虽然我现在就很厉害了 不过我还要百尺竿头更进一步
I'm pretty amazing at it now, but I want to get even better,

764
00:50:10,205 --> 00:50:12,196
我要吹口哨吹到死
make my living out of it.

765
00:50:20,549 --> 00:50:25,816
你知道我还想做什么吗？ 我要侵略邻国
You know what else I would do? I would invade a neighboring country

766
00:50:25,888 --> 00:50:29,824
把我的意愿强加给他们 不管他们愿不愿意
and impose my own ideology, even if they didn't want it!

767
00:50:29,892 --> 00:50:31,826
对你当然简单了，你是国王嘛
Easy for you to say. You're a king.

768
00:50:32,060 --> 00:50:36,053
没错，你只是个等死的脑袋
Yes. And you are only just a sad little head.

769
00:50:36,298 --> 00:50:40,166
不过你死之前，肯定也有想做的事情
There must be something you want to do before you die!

770
00:50:40,235 --> 00:50:44,171
- 是有一件事 - 什么事，告诉我
- There is this one thing. - What? Tell me.

771
00:50:44,239 --> 00:50:47,231
- 哦，我不能说 - 什么事？
- No, I couldn't. - What is it?

772
00:50:47,309 --> 00:50:49,903
我一直都没勇气告诉格罗丽雅 我对她的感觉
I never told Gloria how I feel about her.

773
00:50:49,978 --> 00:50:51,843
什么事情，告诉我！
What is it? Please tell me!

774
00:50:51,914 --> 00:50:55,680
我一直都没勇气告诉格罗丽雅 我对她的感觉
I never had the guts to tell Gloria how I feel about her.

775
00:50:55,751 --> 00:50:57,343
我对她多年的感觉
How I've always felt about her.

776
00:50:57,419 --> 00:50:59,250
好吧，别告诉我！
Fine. Don't tell me!

777
00:51:00,422 --> 00:51:04,518
是女人的事情吗？我可没听见啊
Is it a woman? You didn't tell me it's a woman.

778
00:51:04,593 --> 00:51:08,927
你到底害怕什么？反正你都要死了
What are you afraid of? You're a dead man anyway.

779
00:51:09,264 --> 00:51:11,198
是啊，对啊
Yeah. Yeah.

780
00:51:11,266 --> 00:51:13,200
你说的对
You're right.

781
00:51:13,268 --> 00:51:16,533
你要走到这个女人的面前
You've got to march right up to this woman.

782
00:51:16,605 --> 00:51:19,938
看着她的眼睛，身体前倾
Look her right in the eye. Lean forward.

783
00:51:20,275 --> 00:51:22,766
一点点就好，全靠过去也没关系啦
Just a little, or almost all the way.

784
00:51:23,111 --> 00:51:27,047
然后你让她也靠过来
Then you let her lean forward a little until you're...

785
00:51:27,115 --> 00:51:30,551
直到你们之间只剩一个吻的距离
...just lips' distance away from each other.

786
00:51:30,619 --> 00:51:34,282
然后你告诉他，你有多么讨厌她
Then you tell her how much you hate her.

787
00:51:34,623 --> 00:51:38,855
其实，是多么爱她
Actually, it's more like love her.

788
00:51:38,927 --> 00:51:41,794
哦，你这个小狡猾，大大的狡猾
Oh, you sly dog! Woof, woof!

789
00:51:42,130 --> 00:51:45,463
还是个多情种子啊，听好了
You're a real player. Now listen to me.

790
00:51:45,701 --> 00:51:48,363
你要站起来，听见了吗？
You got to rise up. You hearing me?

791
00:51:48,637 --> 00:51:50,036
- 他没听见 - 我没听见你回答！
- He didn't hear you. - I can't hear you!

792
00:51:50,706 --> 00:51:53,140
- 你要站起来！ - 站起来！
- You got to rise up! - Rising up!

793
00:51:53,709 --> 00:51:56,701
- 离开这个坑！ - 我站起来了！
- Get out of the hole! - I'm rising out of the ground!

794
00:51:56,979 --> 00:51:58,810
- 他站起来了，玛瑞斯 - 我站起来了，玛瑞斯！
- He's rising, Maurice. - I'm rising, Maurice!

795
00:51:59,047 --> 00:52:01,811
- 站起来！ - 你要为这个女人站起来！
- Rising! - You go right up to this woman!

796
00:52:02,718 --> 00:52:03,707
你感觉到了吗？
Do you feel it?

797
00:52:04,152 --> 00:52:06,484
- 走到她的面前 - 告诉她真相！
- Go up to her face! - Tell the truth!

798
00:52:06,822 --> 00:52:11,725
- 我要告诉她！ - 然后告诉她，“宝贝，我爱死你了”
- I'm going to tell her! - Then you say, "Baby, I dig you!"

799
00:52:11,994 --> 00:52:14,986
耶！我要告诉她！我要告诉她！
Yeah! I'm going to do it! I'm going to do it!

800
00:52:15,330 --> 00:52:17,594
我喜欢这个快乐的脑袋
I love that happy little head.

801
00:52:20,068 --> 00:52:21,729
<i>摩托摩托
Moto Moto</i>

802
00:52:24,172 --> 00:52:25,503
<i>摩托摩托
Moto Moto</i>

803
00:52:25,741 --> 00:52:29,177
<i>她爱我 她爱我的眼睛
She loves me She loves my eyes</i>

804
00:52:29,845 --> 00:52:33,178
<i>她爱我 她爱我的大腿
She loves me She loves my thighs</i>

805
00:52:33,515 --> 00:52:35,346
<i>她爱我的球形身材
She loves my roundness</i>

806
00:52:35,684 --> 00:52:39,518
<i>她爱我的又矮又胖 她爱我的丰满强壮
She love that I'm chunky She love that I'm plumpy</i>

807
00:52:39,855 --> 00:52:43,689
<i>她爱我的肌肉发达 她爱我的情趣浪漫
She love my heftiness She love my zestiness</i>

808
00:52:44,026 --> 00:52:47,860
<i>她爱我无时无刻 她爱我无休无止
She love me restlessly She love me forever</i>

809
00:52:48,196 --> 00:52:49,891
<i>她爱我…
She love me...</i>

810
00:52:50,032 --> 00:52:51,624
<i>她就是爱我…
...'cause she love me</i>

811
00:52:51,867 --> 00:52:53,198
摩托摩托…
Moto Moto...

812
00:52:53,702 --> 00:52:56,865
…在我们关系更进一步之前
...before things get too serious, well,

813
00:52:57,205 --> 00:53:01,198
我想知道，如果我要留下来
I was wondering, if I were to, for example, stay here...

814
00:53:01,543 --> 00:53:02,874
我想问你…
...I'd like to ask you...

815
00:53:03,211 --> 00:53:07,545
让你的甜蜜小嘴 在我的耳边轻吟低语吧
Let your candied lips be the messengers to my... ear canal.

816
00:53:08,116 --> 00:53:09,981
我有很多问题要问你
I have so many questions.

817
00:53:10,218 --> 00:53:13,654
我保证，答案都是肯定的
I promise the answer will always be yes.

818
00:53:13,722 --> 00:53:16,384
除非你想要否定的回答
Unless no is required.

819
00:53:16,458 --> 00:53:20,724
那么，你到底觉得我哪里好？
So what is it about me that you find so interesting?

820
00:53:21,463 --> 00:53:24,330
你是我见过的最丰满的女孩
You're the most plumpenest girl I've ever met.

821
00:53:24,399 --> 00:53:26,333
好吧，还有呢
OK. Other than that.

822
00:53:26,401 --> 00:53:28,062
我想想
Let's see.

823
00:53:28,136 --> 00:53:31,128
哦，你很壮实
Yeah, well, you know... you chunky.

824
00:53:32,074 --> 00:53:33,405
这样啊
Right.

825
00:53:35,410 --> 00:53:37,742
天啊，你真高大
My gosh, girl, you huge.

826
00:53:38,013 --> 00:53:39,002
你说过了
You said that.

827
00:53:39,247 --> 00:53:41,238
哦，对哦
Yeah, that's right.

828
00:53:42,084 --> 00:53:43,915
还是无声胜有声吧
We don't have to talk no more.

829
00:53:44,152 --> 00:53:45,346
格罗丽雅！
Gloria!

830
00:53:46,588 --> 00:53:47,680
格罗丽雅！
Gloria.

831
00:53:47,923 --> 00:53:49,083
梅尔曼
Melman.

832
00:53:50,592 --> 00:53:54,926
梅尔曼，我想你见下摩托摩托
Melman, I want you to meet Moto Moto.

833
00:53:55,931 --> 00:54:00,095
摩托摩托，哦，很高兴见到你
Moto Moto. Yeah, nice to meet you.

834
00:54:00,435 --> 00:54:04,064
- 原来你们… - 没关系的，梅尔曼
- I guess I... - It's OK, Melman.

835
00:54:04,139 --> 00:54:05,663
我接受你的道歉了
Apology accepted.

836
00:54:05,741 --> 00:54:10,440
是么，太好了，我就是为这…好的
Oh. Yeah, right, that. That's why I... Good.

837
00:54:11,446 --> 00:54:13,914
好吧，那就这样吧，那我就…
OK. Well, that's it, then.

838
00:54:13,982 --> 00:54:17,110
对了，我们忙着呢
Good. We're kind of busy here, man.

839
00:54:17,452 --> 00:54:19,943
不，不是这样的
No. No, that's not it.

840
00:54:21,456 --> 00:54:24,448
听着，摩托托，你最好对这女孩好一点
Listen, Mototo, you better treat this lady like a queen.

841
00:54:24,960 --> 00:54:28,293
因为你找到了这个世界上最完美的女人
Because you, my friend, you found yourself the perfect woman.

842
00:54:28,530 --> 00:54:31,055
如果我有这么幸运的话
If I was ever so lucky to find the perfect woman,

843
00:54:31,133 --> 00:54:34,899
我一定每天给她送花 当然不是随便什么野花都行，知道吗？
I'd give her flowers every day. And notjust any flowers. OK?

844
00:54:34,970 --> 00:54:38,906
她喜欢兰花，白色的那种 早餐要送到她床上
Her favorites are orchids. White. And breakfast in bed.

845
00:54:38,974 --> 00:54:41,340
六片小麦土司 两面都要涂黄油
Six loaves of wheat toast, butter on both sides.

846
00:54:41,410 --> 00:54:43,071
面包片要去掉，她不喜欢吃
No crust, the way she likes it.

847
00:54:43,311 --> 00:54:46,644
我愿意成为她最知心的朋友 在她伤心难过的时候给她依靠的肩膀
I'd be her shoulder to cry on and her best friend.

848
00:54:46,882 --> 00:54:50,409
我每天都会想着怎么让她开心
I'd spend every day thinking of how to make her laugh.

849
00:54:50,485 --> 00:54:54,148
她有这世界上最美的笑脸
She has the most amazing laugh.

850
00:54:57,492 --> 00:55:00,484
如果我是你，我就会这么做
That's what I would do if I were you.

851
00:55:00,829 --> 00:55:03,161
不过我不是，所以你要替我做了
But I'm not, so you do it.

852
00:55:04,499 --> 00:55:06,160
好吧
OK.

853
00:55:07,169 --> 00:55:08,500
说什么呢？
What?

854
00:55:09,171 --> 00:55:12,004
太感人了
That was beautiful.

855
00:55:12,674 --> 00:55:15,507
对了，我们说到哪了？
Anyways, where were we?

856
00:55:16,011 --> 00:55:17,342
我很“壮实”？
I'm "huge"?

857
00:55:19,181 --> 00:55:20,808
吓到你了吧，马库加？
Surprised to see me, Makunga?

858
00:55:20,882 --> 00:55:24,113
我们来了结恩怨吧，像真正的雄狮那样
Well, I'm here to set things straight, like a real lion!

859
00:55:24,186 --> 00:55:28,520
这拳吃的爽不爽？再吃一记 这是你陷害我的报应
Is this real enough for you? How about this? This is for setting me up!

860
00:55:28,590 --> 00:55:32,583
这拳是因为你抢了我爸爸的工作 这拳是因为你羞辱了我全家
This is for stealing my dad's job! This is for humiliating my family!

861
00:55:32,661 --> 00:55:35,129
让我看起来像个笨蛋！
And making me look like a fool!

862
00:55:52,214 --> 00:55:54,876
满意了？你们就飞走吧
Had enough? Sure, fly away!

863
00:55:55,217 --> 00:55:56,548
懦夫
Coward.

864
00:56:07,729 --> 00:56:10,061
水塘干了
The water. It's gone.

865
00:56:10,398 --> 00:56:12,229
水塘以前从来没干涸过啊
It's never gone dry before.

866
00:56:12,300 --> 00:56:15,167
- 这下大家都要等死了 - 这是怎么回事？
- We'll need a lot more dying holes. - How could this happen?

867
00:56:15,237 --> 00:56:18,502
让开！这是怎么了？
Out of my way! What is going on here?!

868
00:56:18,573 --> 00:56:21,440
水塘干了，水不够喝了
The watering hole is dry! There's barely water for one of us!

869
00:56:21,510 --> 00:56:23,842
- 观察的很仔细嘛，雪莉 - 我叫鲍勃
- Good observation, Shirley. - I'm Bobby.

870
00:56:23,912 --> 00:56:25,402
马库加，我们该怎么办？
Makunga, what do we do?

871
00:56:25,480 --> 00:56:26,970
安静！
Quiet!

872
00:56:27,415 --> 00:56:32,409
听着，要解决危机，我们只有一个办法：
Listen up! I'm afraid there is only one solution to this horrible crisis:

873
00:56:33,421 --> 00:56:35,150
大家来抢好了
We'll all have to fight for it.

874
00:56:35,223 --> 00:56:37,748
- 抢？怎么能这样？ - 太离谱了
- We can't fight for it. - That's crazy.

875
00:56:39,261 --> 00:56:40,751
太不公平了，你肯定赢嘛
That's not fair. You'd win!

876
00:56:40,929 --> 00:56:42,260
就是这意思，雪莉
Exactly, Shirley.

877
00:56:42,430 --> 00:56:43,419
我叫鲍勃…
I'm Bob...

878
00:56:43,999 --> 00:56:47,332
不好意思，各位，生活本来就不公平 现在我话事
Sorry, folks, but life isn't fair. I'm in charge now,

879
00:56:47,602 --> 00:56:50,594
多亏了阿拉凯，那位舞林大狮啊
thanks to Alakay, the dancing lion.

880
00:56:50,872 --> 00:56:54,399
拜托了，马库加，这是保护区里唯一的水源啊
Please, Makunga, this is the only water on the reserve.

881
00:56:54,476 --> 00:56:58,435
如果你渴了，你就得去保护区外找水源了
If you're thirsty, you'll have to look for water off the reserve.

882
00:56:58,780 --> 00:57:01,044
- 保护区外面？ - 太危险了！
- Off the reserve? - It's too dangerous!

883
00:57:01,149 --> 00:57:02,582
盗猎者会把我们都杀掉的
Hunters would shoot us!

884
00:57:02,617 --> 00:57:04,551
从来没有人离开保护区还活着回来的
No one leaves the reserve and survives!

885
00:57:04,619 --> 00:57:06,450
我离开过！
I left the reserve!

886
00:57:06,955 --> 00:57:08,616
我不是还活着？！
And survived.

887
00:57:09,958 --> 00:57:11,892
我有个想法
I can do something about this.

888
00:57:11,960 --> 00:57:16,294
这就和水管堵塞差不多，纽约经常有这事 只要我们往上游走…
Looks like a clogged pipe, like we get in New York. I'll travel upriver...

889
00:57:16,364 --> 00:57:18,491
- 上游？ - 离开保护区？
- Upriver? - Off the reserve?

890
00:57:18,567 --> 00:57:19,693
就凭你？
You?

891
00:57:20,635 --> 00:57:23,763
没错，我会把水道疏通让水源恢复的
Yeah. I'll unclog the pipe and bring back your water.

892
00:57:23,839 --> 00:57:28,970
太好了，我可以帮你整理行李 不过看你戴帽子的衰样，我就知道你已经准备好了
Great! I'd help you pack, but by the looks of that hat, I see you're all set!

893
00:57:29,978 --> 00:57:34,642
好啊，你就笑吧，最好把你的毛都笑秃 我会证明你错了
Fine. Go ahead, laugh. Laugh your mane off. I'll prove you wrong.

894
00:57:35,250 --> 00:57:37,810
也许你可以跳个舞求求雨什么的
Maybe you should try a little rain dance.

895
00:57:43,725 --> 00:57:45,056
祖巴一定知道怎么做的
Zuba would know what to do.

896
00:57:45,327 --> 00:57:47,158
- 祖巴在哪里？ - 你根本不在乎大家的死活
- Where's Zuba? - You don't care about us.

897
00:57:47,395 --> 00:57:49,488
祖巴应该当领导，不是你
Zuba should be in charge, not you.

898
00:57:54,169 --> 00:57:55,727
好吧，好吧！
All right, fine!

899
00:57:56,004 --> 00:57:59,496
为了谨慎起见 我会向祖巴咨询的！
As an added measure, I will consult with Zuba!

900
00:58:06,014 --> 00:58:07,345
马蒂？
Marty?

901
00:58:16,358 --> 00:58:18,189
马蒂？
Hey! Marty!

902
00:58:23,031 --> 00:58:24,521
马蒂？
Marty?

903
00:58:27,369 --> 00:58:28,961
马蒂
Marty.

904
00:58:29,104 --> 00:58:30,696
他的水果帽哪儿来的？
Where'd you get the fruity hat?

905
00:58:31,039 --> 00:58:33,200
不好意思，不好意思！
Excuse me! Excuse me!

906
00:58:33,541 --> 00:58:36,533
马蒂在吗？
Hi. Is Marty in there?

907
00:58:37,212 --> 00:58:39,373
有人看见马蒂了吗？
Anyone seen Marty?

908
00:58:41,650 --> 00:58:43,550
马蒂在哪？
Which one of us is Marty?

909
00:58:44,052 --> 00:58:46,714
好吧，如果你们看见他
All right. Well, if you see him,

910
00:58:46,788 --> 00:58:49,222
请告诉他 他的朋友阿历克斯来跟他告别
tell him his friend Alex came to say goodbye.

911
00:58:49,291 --> 00:58:52,055
告别？别走嘛，你要去哪啊？
Goodbye? Don't go. Where are you going?

912
00:58:52,127 --> 00:58:55,494
- 我们可以去吗？ - 不行，这是我一个人的事情
- Can we come? - No. I have to do this alone.

913
00:58:55,563 --> 00:58:57,724
你不能出保护区！
You can't leave the reserve!

914
00:59:09,144 --> 00:59:10,475
你在干什么呀？
What are you doing?

915
00:59:10,745 --> 00:59:12,906
- 他们会连你帽子都抢的 - 盗猎者到处都是
- They'll get your hat. - Hunters are everywhere!

916
00:59:13,915 --> 00:59:15,405
你要去把帽子留下好不好
Could you leave the hat?

917
00:59:15,483 --> 00:59:17,144
马蒂！我知道你在里面
Marty! I know you're in there.

918
00:59:18,253 --> 00:59:21,245
离开之前，我有些话想对你说
Before I go, I got something I want to say.

919
00:59:22,257 --> 00:59:24,521
你一直都是个好朋友
You've been a great friend.

920
00:59:24,592 --> 00:59:28,084
你总是帮我找到问题的积极面
You've helped me so often to see the bright side of my problems

921
00:59:28,163 --> 00:59:30,028
我却从来没有想过你也有自己的烦恼
that I never think of you having any.

922
00:59:31,433 --> 00:59:33,924
在你需要我的时候 我没有在你身边支持你
I wasn't there for you when you needed me.

923
00:59:34,436 --> 00:59:36,267
就像在动物园时一样
Just like back at the zoo.

924
00:59:37,172 --> 00:59:41,438
我这算哪门子的朋友？ 真是逊毙了
What kind of friend does that make me? A pretty lousy friend, I guess.

925
00:59:42,277 --> 00:59:43,938
我只是想让你知道…
I just want you to know that I...

926
00:59:44,946 --> 00:59:46,777
你是我的真心朋友
You're one in a million.

927
00:59:47,282 --> 00:59:49,113
太感人了
This is touching.

928
00:59:49,184 --> 00:59:50,617
真是太感人了
It is touching.

929
00:59:50,952 --> 00:59:54,444
你能转过身来，让我当面告诉你吗？
So could you turn around so I can tell you to your face?

930
00:59:55,123 --> 00:59:57,114
找到你了！
That's right. Gotcha!

931
00:59:57,459 --> 01:00:00,053
我看到你了，没错，就是你
I see you in there! Yeah, you.

932
01:00:00,128 --> 01:00:02,062
没错，就是你
You, right there.

933
01:00:02,130 --> 01:00:06,396
第二十排左数第二百零三个
Twelfth row, two hundred and third from the left.

934
01:00:06,468 --> 01:00:07,867
找到你了，马蒂
That's you, Marty.

935
01:00:08,303 --> 01:00:09,964
知道是你
I know it's you.

936
01:00:11,806 --> 01:00:13,865
你知道你特别在哪吗？
Know what makes you special?

937
01:00:14,209 --> 01:00:18,646
他们都是白黑相间的 而你是黑白相间的
These guys are white with black stripes. You're black with white stripes.

938
01:00:18,880 --> 01:00:20,541
你是个天生的梦想家，马蒂
You're a dreamer, Marty.

939
01:00:20,815 --> 01:00:24,478
一直都是，而且你对音乐很有品味
Always have been. You have great taste in music

940
01:00:24,819 --> 01:00:27,151
交朋友却逊得很
and horrible taste in friends.

941
01:00:27,489 --> 01:00:30,652
我不是说梅尔曼和格罗丽雅 我说的是我自己
Well, not Melman and Gloria, but me.

942
01:00:32,994 --> 01:00:34,427
好吧，我跟你去
OK, I'm in.

943
01:00:34,496 --> 01:00:36,828
马蒂，你不能去
Marty, you can't come with me.

944
01:00:36,898 --> 01:00:38,661
这不是你说了算的
You don't have a choice.

945
01:00:43,505 --> 01:00:46,167
- 那边有人类！ - 你们真是疯了，回来啊！
- People are out there! - You're crazy! Come back!

946
01:00:46,508 --> 01:00:48,169
他们会抓住你们的
The people will get you!

947
01:00:48,510 --> 01:00:50,569
帽子可别丢了啊
Don't lose the hat!

948
01:00:51,446 --> 01:00:52,777
帽子，永别了
Bye, hat!

949
01:00:56,351 --> 01:00:57,443
有水吗？
Any water?

950
01:00:58,353 --> 01:01:01,186
没有，还是金子和钻石
No, just more diamonds and gold.

951
01:01:06,461 --> 01:01:07,860
大家别放弃希望
Don't give up hope.

952
01:01:07,929 --> 01:01:10,830
大家听着！我来拯救你们了！
Listen up! I will help you!

953
01:01:10,899 --> 01:01:14,027
想要水回来，出路只有一条
There's only one way to get your precious water.

954
01:01:14,602 --> 01:01:17,366
我，你们敬爱的国王朱利安
I, your beloved King Julien

955
01:01:17,872 --> 01:01:22,536
只要给我的好朋友水神们送点祭品就有水了
must simply make a small sacrifice to my good friends, the water gods,

956
01:01:22,877 --> 01:01:25,710
他们就住在火山里！
in the volcano!

957
01:01:29,217 --> 01:01:30,377
这有什么用？
What does that do?

958
01:01:30,618 --> 01:01:33,280
有什么用？问得好
What does that do? Excellent question.

959
01:01:33,555 --> 01:01:36,649
只要把我的祭品送进火山口
My sacrifice goes in the volcano.

960
01:01:36,724 --> 01:01:40,717
我的好朋友水神享用了祭品之后
The friendly gods eat up my sacrifice.

961
01:01:41,062 --> 01:01:43,223
“很好吃，谢谢你的祭品啊”
"Thank you for the sacrifice."

962
01:01:43,298 --> 01:01:46,165
“多吃点嘛” “不，我已经吃饱了”
"Here, have another." "No, I've had enough."

963
01:01:46,234 --> 01:01:48,600
“你不多吃点就太见外了”
"I'll be insulted unless you have another."

964
01:01:48,670 --> 01:01:51,104
“我已经吃饱了”
"I don't want another sacrifice!"

965
01:01:51,172 --> 01:01:54,232
“你看看你，瘦成这样” “我说我已经吃饱了，你聋了吗？！”
"Look at you! You're skinny!" "No! I've had enough!"

966
01:01:56,744 --> 01:01:59,838
水神们享用了祭品了之后非常开心
The gods eat the sacrifice. They are grateful.

967
01:01:59,948 --> 01:02:03,782
他们会给我水 我再把水给你们就好了
They give me some water, and then I give it to you.

968
01:02:03,818 --> 01:02:05,080
什么？
What?

969
01:02:05,520 --> 01:02:06,646
有用吗？
Does it work?

970
01:02:07,088 --> 01:02:09,420
当然没！我是说，当然有啦
No! I mean, yes.

971
01:02:09,924 --> 01:02:11,414
你说呢，莫里斯？
Well, Maurice?

972
01:02:11,759 --> 01:02:14,091
呃，一半一半吧
Ah, it's fifty-fifty.

973
01:02:15,096 --> 01:02:16,927
我们同意！
We'll do it!

974
01:02:17,932 --> 01:02:19,263
太好了！
Excellent!

975
01:02:19,934 --> 01:02:23,802
现在我需要有人到火山口里去
Now all I need is someone who would like to go into the volcano

976
01:02:23,872 --> 01:02:25,863
当水神们的祭品
and get eaten by gods.

977
01:02:26,608 --> 01:02:29,168
有人愿意去吗？举手啊
Any hands! Hands, anybody!

978
01:02:29,244 --> 01:02:32,771
好吧，这里有没有还没找到过真爱…
I need someone, perhaps who has never found love,

979
01:02:33,114 --> 01:02:38,017
面对死亡无所畏惧的真心英雄？
who could look death straight in the eyeball. A real, genuine hero.

980
01:02:38,086 --> 01:02:40,111
- 我来当祭品吧！ - 梅尔曼？
- I'll do it. - Melman?

981
01:02:49,631 --> 01:02:53,294
赶紧走，等大家都恢复理智可就不好
Hurry up! Before we all come to our senses!

982
01:02:54,369 --> 01:02:56,360
梅尔曼，你怎么了？
Melman, what is wrong with you?

983
01:02:56,638 --> 01:03:01,302
反正我也还是将死之鹿了 如果我的死能求来水，我死也瞑目了
I'm dying anyway. If there's a chance it'll get you water, it's worth it.

984
01:03:01,643 --> 01:03:03,406
你脑子秀逗了吗？
Are you nuts?

985
01:03:03,478 --> 01:03:06,174
我只是想你知道，在动物园的时候…
I want you to know, back at the zoo,

986
01:03:06,247 --> 01:03:09,580
让我能活下去的不是医生的处方
it was never the doctors or prescriptions that kept me going.

987
01:03:09,817 --> 01:03:11,910
从来都只因为你
It was always you.

988
01:03:11,986 --> 01:03:14,420
只要每天都能看到你
Seeing you every day.

989
01:03:14,489 --> 01:03:16,650
我就有活下去的勇气
That's what kept me going.

990
01:03:20,328 --> 01:03:22,319
梅尔曼，等等！
Melman! Wait!

991
01:03:23,398 --> 01:03:28,062
梅尔曼！梅尔曼！梅尔曼！
Melman! Melman! Melman!

992
01:03:30,838 --> 01:03:33,329
你打算就这么一直生闷气吗？
You going to mope like this all day?

993
01:03:34,175 --> 01:03:35,665
别和我哼哼
Don't "hmph" me.

994
01:03:35,944 --> 01:03:39,607
-听着，祖巴，这是个奇迹
Listen, Zuba. A miracle happened.

995
01:03:39,681 --> 01:03:44,550
我们的孩子回到我们身边了 你还不满意吗？
Our son came back to us. How come that is not good enough for you?

996
01:03:44,619 --> 01:03:46,746
你说什么呢，雌性！
What are you saying, woman?

997
01:03:47,689 --> 01:03:51,853
我们曾失去过他一次，祖巴 我们不能再失去他了
We lost him once, Zuba. Let's not lose him again.

998
01:04:01,202 --> 01:04:02,533
祖巴！
Zuba!

999
01:04:03,538 --> 01:04:05,199
- 祖巴！ - 滚开！
- Zuba! - Get out of here!

1000
01:04:05,440 --> 01:04:07,101
你有何贵干？
What do you want?

1001
01:04:07,175 --> 01:04:08,369
出事了
It's awful.

1002
01:04:09,043 --> 01:04:10,772
水塘干了
The watering hole is dried up.

1003
01:04:10,845 --> 01:04:13,780
干了？不可能
Dried up? That's impossible!

1004
01:04:13,848 --> 01:04:15,713
一滴都没剩！
There's nothing left!

1005
01:04:15,783 --> 01:04:19,549
你是狮王，马库加 你有什么办法？
You're alpha lion, Makunga. What are you gonna do about it?

1006
01:04:19,621 --> 01:04:23,853
你的儿子，阿拉凯，他说他能解决 他往上游去了
Your son, Alakay, he said he could fix it. He's gone upriver.

1007
01:04:23,925 --> 01:04:25,517
-他出了保护区了？ - 不会吧！
- Off the reserve?! - No!

1008
01:04:25,593 --> 01:04:28,323
我曾想阻止他 我跟他说这纯粹是自杀
I tried to stop him. I told him it was suicide.

1009
01:04:28,396 --> 01:04:30,660
但是他一心想要证明自己给你看
He was determined to prove himself to you.

1010
01:04:31,899 --> 01:04:34,800
你留在这，以防万一他回来
You stay here, in case he comes back!

1011
01:04:37,405 --> 01:04:39,066
快去啊，祖巴！
Hurry, Zuba!

1012
01:04:42,343 --> 01:04:44,004
我喉咙太干了
I'm so parched.

1013
01:04:49,584 --> 01:04:52,747
这地方是不是越来越毛骨悚然了？
Is this place starting to freak you out?

1014
01:04:52,820 --> 01:04:57,348
我们分头走，找到问题所在 猎人们不会发现我们的
We'll slip in, find the problem. Hunters will never know we were here.

1015
01:04:57,425 --> 01:04:59,154
为什么这事只有我们做？
Why are we doing this?

1016
01:04:59,427 --> 01:05:02,760
这样我爸爸会觉得我…
Maybe my dad will think I'm...

1017
01:05:03,264 --> 01:05:05,630
我想让他知道我是只真正的雄狮
I want to show him I'm a real lion.

1018
01:05:05,700 --> 01:05:08,863
那你现在是什么？巧克力狮子？
As opposed to a chocolate lion.

1019
01:05:08,936 --> 01:05:14,374
我知道这听起来难以置信 不过真正的狮子貌似是不跳舞的
I know this may sound hard to believe, but apparently, lions don't dance.

1020
01:05:14,442 --> 01:05:15,602
什么？！
What?!

1021
01:05:16,511 --> 01:05:18,376
至少我爸爸是这么想的
As far as my dad is concerned.

1022
01:05:18,446 --> 01:05:21,040
可你是个明星啊，至少人们是这么想的
As far as people are concerned, you're a hit.

1023
01:05:21,282 --> 01:05:24,445
那是在纽约，这是在非洲 标准不一样
In New York. This is Africa... much tougher crowd.

1024
01:05:24,519 --> 01:05:26,510
马蒂，就是这里了！
Marty, this is it!

1025
01:05:27,622 --> 01:05:30,113
就是这里堵塞了
This is the clog! Come on.

1026
01:05:37,131 --> 01:05:39,292
水都在这啊
Well, there's the water.

1027
01:05:41,469 --> 01:05:43,960
注意隐蔽，看那边
Stay down. Look at that.

1028
01:05:44,305 --> 01:05:46,637
一针正针，两针反针
Knit one, purl two.

1029
01:05:46,708 --> 01:05:47,800
是她
It's her.

1030
01:05:47,875 --> 01:05:49,570
- 这样对吗？ - 织的很好
- Is this right? - Very good.

1031
01:05:49,644 --> 01:05:51,578
奶奶，你慢点
Nana, slow down.

1032
01:05:51,646 --> 01:05:54,410
你这都织成麻袋了
You're a little tangled, aren't you?

1033
01:05:54,482 --> 01:05:56,814
别扯，让我来吧
No, don't pull. I'll do it.

1034
01:05:57,752 --> 01:05:59,219
我们需要炸药，你有吗？
We need dynamite. Got any?

1035
01:05:59,487 --> 01:06:03,480
哦，糟了，我今天早上刚用完！
Oh, snap! I just used my last stick this morning!

1036
01:06:05,760 --> 01:06:07,489
- 野蛮人啊！ - 快执行躲避战术！
- Savages! - Evasive maneuvers!

1037
01:06:07,762 --> 01:06:10,128
- 蛇形躲避，用蛇形！ - 乌贼型躲避
- Serpentine, serpentine! - Squiggly squid maneuver!

1038
01:06:10,198 --> 01:06:12,996
锯齿形，锯齿形躲避！
Zag, zig-zag, zig ziggy zag!

1039
01:06:13,334 --> 01:06:15,666
不对，不对，用乌贼型！
No, no! Squiggly squid!

1040
01:06:16,003 --> 01:06:17,095
残影躲避
Etch A Sketch!

1041
01:06:17,338 --> 01:06:20,330
太复杂啦！章鱼型，章鱼型躲避！
That's too complex! Octopus, octopus!

1042
01:06:22,510 --> 01:06:25,843
- 快跑，马蒂！ - 我不能把你一人丢下！
- Run, Marty! - I can't leave you here!

1043
01:06:26,581 --> 01:06:29,914
去找人帮忙！用乌贼型躲避！ 快点去！用乌贼型躲避！
Go get help! Squiggly squid maneuver! Go! Go! Squiggly squid!

1044
01:06:30,184 --> 01:06:33,119
残影躲避！残影躲避！
Etch A Sketch! Etch A Sketch!

1045
01:06:34,389 --> 01:06:37,449
<i>拯救我们！ 我们爱你！
Save us We love you</i>

1046
01:06:37,525 --> 01:06:38,856
没问题
OK.

1047
01:06:39,193 --> 01:06:41,855
没问题，不怕
OK, OK, OK.

1048
01:06:48,803 --> 01:06:50,566
<i>- 拯救我们 - 梅尔曼
- Save us - Melman</i>

1049
01:06:50,638 --> 01:06:52,367
<i>- 我们爱你 - 梅尔曼
- We love you - Melman</i>

1050
01:06:52,440 --> 01:06:53,429
<i>拯救我们
Save us</i>

1051
01:06:53,508 --> 01:06:55,942
没问题，跳下去就可以，不怕不怕
OK, here we go. OK, OK.

1052
01:06:56,010 --> 01:06:58,001
<i>- 梅尔曼 - 我们爱你
- Melman - We love you</i>

1053
01:06:58,079 --> 01:06:59,637
<i>- 梅尔曼 - 拯救我们
- Melman - Save us</i>

1054
01:06:59,747 --> 01:07:02,409
我来了，我来了
Here we go! Here we go!

1055
01:07:03,151 --> 01:07:05,483
- 怎么这么热闹？ - 乔？
- What's all the hoopla about? - Joe?

1056
01:07:05,720 --> 01:07:08,211
巫医乔？我们以为你早死了！
Joe the Witch Doctor? We thought you were dead!

1057
01:07:08,489 --> 01:07:11,947
我也以为我已经死了 后来发现原来我全身都是斑点啊
So did I. Then I realized I'm covered in brown spots.

1058
01:07:12,226 --> 01:07:15,059
那么梅尔曼也没得绝症啊！
So Melman's not dying!

1059
01:07:15,563 --> 01:07:18,225
- 梅尔曼没得绝症？ - 天啊，不会吧！
- Melman's not dying! - Oh, no!

1060
01:07:18,566 --> 01:07:19,555
梅尔曼！
Melman!

1061
01:07:19,834 --> 01:07:21,165
让开！
Move!

1062
01:07:21,402 --> 01:07:25,168
别跳啊，梅尔曼，别跳，别犯傻！
Don't do this! Julien, stop this! This is crazy!

1063
01:07:25,239 --> 01:07:30,108
现在丢长颈鹿到火山里去求雨算是犯傻啦？
Oh, suddenly throwing a giraffe into a volcano to make water is crazy!

1064
01:07:30,178 --> 01:07:31,167
就是！
Yes!

1065
01:07:33,748 --> 01:07:37,707
- 拜托，梅尔曼，别跳啊！ - 格罗丽雅？
- Please, Melman! Stop! - Gloria?

1066
01:07:37,785 --> 01:07:39,844
- 你不能跳下去！ - 为什么？
- You can't do this! - Why not?

1067
01:07:40,087 --> 01:07:41,418
因为…
Because...

1068
01:08:00,675 --> 01:08:02,336
你就是不能跳，梅尔曼
You can't do this, Melman.

1069
01:08:02,610 --> 01:08:04,271
首先，我的心都碎了
First, that hurts.

1070
01:08:04,545 --> 01:08:07,673
其次，反正我只有18个小时可活了
Second, I've only got 18 hours to live, anyway.

1071
01:08:07,748 --> 01:08:10,273
梅尔曼，一定要问清楚…
Melman, I gotta know...

1072
01:08:11,452 --> 01:08:13,943
你跟我说的那些话，都是真心的吗？
...did you mean those things you said about me?

1073
01:08:14,956 --> 01:08:16,355
当然是真心的
Of course I did.

1074
01:08:16,691 --> 01:08:18,784
- 太离谱了 - 离谱吗？
- That's crazy. - It is?

1075
01:08:21,462 --> 01:08:25,455
真正离谱的是 我居然只有在到了世界的尽头的时候…
It's crazy to think I had to go halfway around the world...

1076
01:08:26,033 --> 01:08:28,797
…才发现真爱其实…
...to find out the perfect guy for me

1077
01:08:29,136 --> 01:08:30,797
一直在我身旁
lived right next door.

1078
01:08:31,806 --> 01:08:34,138
看来剩下的18个小时
Then it's you and me, neighbor.

1079
01:08:34,375 --> 01:08:37,037
我可以没有遗憾了
You and me for the next 18 hours.

1080
01:08:37,311 --> 01:08:39,472
时间再短暂 真爱永流传
I'll take whatever you got.

1081
01:08:43,818 --> 01:08:47,083
- 玛瑞斯，怎么回事？ - 胖妞找到真爱了
- Maurice, what happened? - I believe the fat lady has sung.

1082
01:08:47,154 --> 01:08:49,987
- 这儿怎么回事？ - 马蒂？
- What's going on here? - Marty!

1083
01:08:50,258 --> 01:08:53,989
阿历克斯有麻烦了！ 我们快去上游救他！
Alex is in big trouble! We got to get upriver fast!

1084
01:08:54,262 --> 01:08:56,492
- 坐飞机去怎么样？ - 太好了，走吧！
- What about the plane? - Perfect! Come on!

1085
01:08:59,267 --> 01:09:03,067
不满足我们的条件，大家就不开工
The plane won't be fixed until the suits meet our demands.

1086
01:09:03,137 --> 01:09:04,832
怎么样，给不给产假？
Now, maternity leave.

1087
01:09:04,906 --> 01:09:08,398
产假？你们都是爷们啊
Maternity leave? You're all males.

1088
01:09:08,476 --> 01:09:10,967
我们要用飞机执行营救任务
We need that plane for a rescue mission.

1089
01:09:11,045 --> 01:09:13,980
工会没解体之前你们别想了
There's nothing I can do until we bust up this union.

1090
01:09:14,048 --> 01:09:17,415
如果还不把飞机修好，我就让你们都解体！
I'll bust up all of you if you don't get this plane going.

1091
01:09:17,485 --> 01:09:21,819
你没看见这些民工正罢工呢吗？ 没有产假！
Can't you see these commies have my hands tied? No maternity leave.

1092
01:09:24,392 --> 01:09:29,386
也许有人不希望这些照片流传出去吧
Maybe a certain someone wouldn't want these blowing around on the savanna.

1093
01:09:38,506 --> 01:09:41,168
好吧，给你们产假
All right. You get your maternity leave.

1094
01:09:42,577 --> 01:09:43,908
总算好了
Finally.

1095
01:09:48,583 --> 01:09:51,848
你们带我去哪？ 你们要干什么？
Where we headed? What's going on? Where are we going?

1096
01:09:51,919 --> 01:09:55,582
别这样，拜托了，别把我架在上面
Oh, no! Please! Don't put me there! No!

1097
01:09:55,923 --> 01:09:57,584
你们搞错了
This is wrong.

1098
01:09:57,658 --> 01:10:01,219
看见没，你们都是“幸存者” （美国知名真人秀节目）
You see? You are survivors.

1099
01:10:01,295 --> 01:10:05,095
现在，尝尝烤狮子怎么样？
Now, how about a nice lion casserole?

1100
01:10:05,533 --> 01:10:07,057
我们不能吃狮子
You can't eat a lion.

1101
01:10:07,134 --> 01:10:09,068
别担心，尝起来和鸡肉差不多
Don't worry, it tastes like chicken.

1102
01:10:09,136 --> 01:10:11,434
不要啊，别听她的
No, no, no. Don't listen to her.

1103
01:10:12,273 --> 01:10:14,434
她已经疯了，你们清醒点
She's out of her mind, people!

1104
01:10:16,577 --> 01:10:18,272
我也是纽约来的啊！
I'm from New York City!

1105
01:10:18,546 --> 01:10:21,014
是我啊，我是中央公园的阿历克斯啊！
It's me, Alex the lion! From Central Park!

1106
01:10:28,623 --> 01:10:29,612
爸爸！
Dad!

1107
01:10:30,558 --> 01:10:34,790
你脑袋被大象踩了么？ 跑这儿来干嘛？
What were you thinking, son? You got no business being out here!

1108
01:10:36,797 --> 01:10:38,628
你躲在我后面
Stay behind me.

1109
01:10:38,699 --> 01:10:41,896
他们只是纽约人，有点粗鲁受了惊吓而已
They're New Yorkers. They're just rude and frightened people.

1110
01:10:42,136 --> 01:10:43,467
躲在后面！
Stay back!

1111
01:10:43,804 --> 01:10:45,795
你们还想不想吃晚饭了？
You'd let your dinner get away?

1112
01:10:52,146 --> 01:10:55,479
- 你搞什么？儿子 - 看我的
- What are you doing? - The only thing I know how to do.

1113
01:10:59,720 --> 01:11:00,709
搞什么鬼？
What the heck?

1114
01:11:05,826 --> 01:11:08,158
嗨，这些动作真眼熟
Hey, I know those moves.

1115
01:11:08,596 --> 01:11:09,654
是阿历克斯？
Alex?

1116
01:11:13,167 --> 01:11:15,397
- 是狮子阿历克斯啊！ - 中央公园的那只！
- It's Alex the lion! - From Central Park!

1117
01:11:15,736 --> 01:11:17,101
真的是阿历克斯！
It is Alex!

1118
01:11:17,171 --> 01:11:19,833
世界上只有一只狮子舞跳的这么好！
Only one lion can move like that!

1119
01:11:25,179 --> 01:11:26,510
真帅啊！
He's beautiful.

1120
01:11:26,747 --> 01:11:27,736
简直难以置信
I can't believe it.

1121
01:11:34,522 --> 01:11:36,683
他怎么做到的？
How does he do that?

1122
01:11:49,704 --> 01:11:50,762
你干什么？
What are you doing?

1123
01:11:51,038 --> 01:11:53,700
我和儿子一起跳舞啊，我想是
I'm dancing with my son! I think.

1124
01:11:54,041 --> 01:11:55,531
不要想，爸爸，要感觉！
Don't think, Dad. Feel!

1125
01:11:56,544 --> 01:11:58,205
蝴蝶穿花！
Butterfly!

1126
01:12:00,881 --> 01:12:02,712
我感觉到了！我感觉到了！
I'm feeling it! I'm feeling it!

1127
01:12:14,562 --> 01:12:16,553
嗷！
Roar!

1128
01:12:26,574 --> 01:12:29,566
跳的真不错，现在该吃饭了！
That was beautiful. Now let's eat!

1129
01:12:29,910 --> 01:12:31,138
爸爸，当心！
Dad, look out!

1130
01:12:33,247 --> 01:12:34,407
这是…
What the...

1131
01:12:34,682 --> 01:12:36,240
阿历克斯！快上去！
Alex! Get in!

1132
01:12:36,484 --> 01:12:40,079
她手里有枪，快走啊！
She's got a gun! Get out while we can!

1133
01:12:40,354 --> 01:12:41,946
- 什么？ - 她手里有枪！
- What? - She's got a gun!

1134
01:12:42,089 --> 01:12:44,421
快走！传话过去！
Get out while we can! Pass it on!

1135
01:12:48,095 --> 01:12:52,589
他说炸掉大坝让大家开心一下吧！
He said let's have some fun and take out the dam. Basset hound.

1136
01:12:52,833 --> 01:12:55,927
机长，阿历克斯说要炸掉水坝
Skipper! Alex wants to take out the dam.

1137
01:12:56,170 --> 01:12:58,502
没问题，他就来当炸弹吧！
All right! But it's his funeral.

1138
01:12:59,607 --> 01:13:02,440
- 飞向水坝！ - 明白，机长！
- Hard to port! - Aye-aye, Skippy!

1139
01:13:02,777 --> 01:13:05,268
加油！加油啊！
Bring it on! Bring it on!

1140
01:13:11,619 --> 01:13:13,951
回来！那是我的晚饭！
Come back! That's my dinner!

1141
01:13:14,188 --> 01:13:15,849
科瓦斯基，全速前进
Kowalski, full throttle.

1142
01:13:18,459 --> 01:13:19,448
音乐！
Music!

1143
01:13:20,528 --> 01:13:23,053
- 我喜欢这首歌 - 经典就是经典
- I like this song. - It never gets old.

1144
01:13:23,297 --> 01:13:27,199
的确琅琅上口嘛 注意！降低高度！
It does have a catchy hook. Come about! Bring her in low!

1145
01:13:27,968 --> 01:13:31,460
各位抓紧扶稳，我们去搞垮水坝！
Hold onto your skirts! It's dam-busting time!

1146
01:13:32,640 --> 01:13:35,803
抓紧啦，我们来啦！
Hold on tight, baby! Here we go!

1147
01:13:36,977 --> 01:13:39,639
告诉他们别这样！升上去！不然我们会死的！
Tell them no! Pull up! They'll kill us!

1148
01:13:39,880 --> 01:13:42,872
肯定有别的办法的！传话过去！
There's got to be another way! Pass it on!

1149
01:13:46,086 --> 01:13:50,318
他们说别爬升，让我们死吧，这是唯一的办法了
They say no pull up. Kill us. There's no other way. Basset hound.

1150
01:13:50,558 --> 01:13:51,889
你没搞错吗？
Are you sure?

1151
01:13:52,159 --> 01:13:56,653
真是舍生取义啊
Men, there is no sacrifice greater than someone else's.

1152
01:13:56,997 --> 01:13:58,328
这不是真的！医务兵！
No! Medic!

1153
01:14:03,003 --> 01:14:04,163
加速！
Ramming speed!

1154
01:14:08,909 --> 01:14:10,001
来吧！
Bring it on!

1155
01:14:12,346 --> 01:14:14,177
讨厌的小猫
Bad kitties.

1156
01:14:21,856 --> 01:14:24,848
我不知道祭品怎么没效果
I don't know why the sacrifice didn't work.

1157
01:14:25,192 --> 01:14:27,524
理论没错啊
The science seemed so solid.

1158
01:14:27,928 --> 01:14:32,695
如果我不是口哨吹的太好的话 我自己就去当祭品了
I'd jump right in that volcano if I wasn't so good at whistling.

1159
01:14:42,376 --> 01:14:44,367
是您！我找到您了！
It's you! I found you!

1160
01:14:44,612 --> 01:14:45,601
莫特？
Mort?

1161
01:14:48,382 --> 01:14:50,043
大坏鱼！
Bad fishy!

1162
01:15:00,060 --> 01:15:01,960
水神不知道喜不喜欢海鲜
I wonder if the gods like seafood.

1163
01:15:02,296 --> 01:15:03,888
拭目以待吧
Let's find out.

1164
01:15:05,399 --> 01:15:06,730
看啊 ，玛瑞斯
Look, Maurice.

1165
01:15:09,169 --> 01:15:10,898
- 真灵验啊 - 我成功了
- That was quick. - I did it!

1166
01:15:11,238 --> 01:15:13,729
我成功！我成功了！
I did it! I did it!

1167
01:15:15,075 --> 01:15:16,064
是啊，你立功了！
OK, you did it!

1168
01:15:16,310 --> 01:15:18,073
噢！太好了！
Oh, yes!!

1169
01:15:44,204 --> 01:15:45,193
看啊！
Look!

1170
01:15:45,773 --> 01:15:47,604
- 是阿拉凯！ - 是祖巴！
- It's Alakay! - It's Zuba!

1171
01:15:48,776 --> 01:15:50,107
你们成功了！
You did it!

1172
01:15:50,611 --> 01:15:52,602
阿拉凯，祖巴，你们成功了！
Alakay, Zuba, you did it!

1173
01:15:58,953 --> 01:16:00,944
祖巴！阿拉凯！
Zuba! Alakay!

1174
01:16:01,555 --> 01:16:02,544
你们回来了！
You're back!

1175
01:16:04,358 --> 01:16:06,349
你们没事我真是太高兴了
I'm so glad you're safe!

1176
01:16:07,294 --> 01:16:08,955
让开
Out of my way.

1177
01:16:09,630 --> 01:16:11,962
好吧，好吧
Well, well, well.

1178
01:16:12,967 --> 01:16:17,461
如果我没记错的话，你不当狮王了
You know, Zuba, if I remember correctly, you quit the pride.

1179
01:16:17,805 --> 01:16:19,636
而你，被逐出狮群了
And you were kicked out.

1180
01:16:19,907 --> 01:16:23,638
所以别指望你们能咸鱼翻身
So don't think that this changes anything.

1181
01:16:23,911 --> 01:16:28,712
没错，您是大王，我们还专门给您带回来了礼物
You're right. In fact, we humbly present you with this token of appreciation.

1182
01:16:28,983 --> 01:16:31,247
一个雄狮味十足的包包 这在纽约可是很流行的
A man bag. Very popular where Im from.

1183
01:16:31,318 --> 01:16:33,684
- 我真不知道说什么好 - 您带了可以尽显雄风，还能装东西
- Don't know what to say. - Still be tough and carry your stuff.

1184
01:16:33,754 --> 01:16:38,919
这背带可调的？真不错 我散步时挎着可真是太时髦了
Does the strap adjust? This will go very nicely for me when I go out hiking.

1185
01:16:39,159 --> 01:16:41,150
不过你们还是要被流放
But you're still banished.

1186
01:16:41,395 --> 01:16:43,158
我们知道你会这么说
We figured you'd say that.

1187
01:16:45,332 --> 01:16:47,493
我的包包！
My handbag!

1188
01:16:48,268 --> 01:16:49,735
你这讨厌的小猫！
You bad kitty!

1189
01:16:53,640 --> 01:16:55,198
不要啊！不要啊！
No, no, no, no, no, no, no!

1190
01:17:05,753 --> 01:17:07,744
你证明了自己，儿子
You deserve this, son.

1191
01:17:08,856 --> 01:17:11,017
这荣耀该是你的
Welcome to the pride.

1192
01:17:15,629 --> 01:17:18,530
谢谢，老爸，不过这该是你的
Thanks, Dad. But this belongs to you.

1193
01:17:18,866 --> 01:17:21,357
不，儿子，是我们的！
No, son. To us!

1194
01:17:26,540 --> 01:17:30,704
我的儿子！纽约之王！
My son! The King of New York!

1195
01:17:32,379 --> 01:17:34,370
我的好孩子！
That's my baby!

1196
01:17:41,722 --> 01:17:44,714
真爱超越一切界限
Love transcends all differences.

1197
01:17:45,392 --> 01:17:49,726
今天我们在这里欢聚 见证这样的爱情
We are gathered here today to celebrate such a love.

1198
01:17:50,564 --> 01:17:53,897
不管人生起落，你们是否都会终生厮守？
Do you take each other, for better or for worse?

1199
01:17:57,471 --> 01:17:58,665
还是“起”吧
For better, please.

1200
01:18:00,074 --> 01:18:02,565
你们这对真是…好奇怪啊
What a beautiful, weird couple!

1201
01:18:02,910 --> 01:18:04,741
不会长久的
That's not going to last.

1202
01:18:05,913 --> 01:18:07,813
我可以亲下新娘吗？
Can I kiss the bride?

1203
01:18:08,148 --> 01:18:09,740
当然不行！音乐！
No! Music!

1204
01:18:10,484 --> 01:18:11,576
- 支架！ - 检查完毕！
- Struts. - Check.

1205
01:18:11,919 --> 01:18:12,908
- 机翼！ - 检查完毕！
- Flaps! - Check.

1206
01:18:13,153 --> 01:18:14,916
- 钻石和黄金 - 检查完毕
- Diamonds and gold. - Check.

1207
01:18:17,424 --> 01:18:19,085
- 再见咯 - 我们会想你们的！
- Bye-bye! - We'll miss you!

1208
01:18:19,159 --> 01:18:20,353
再见啦！
See you later!

1209
01:18:20,427 --> 01:18:23,362
在蒙特卡洛度完蜜月后，我们会回来的
We'll be back after the honeymoon in Monte Carlo,

1210
01:18:23,430 --> 01:18:25,261
也许是金子花光的时候
or whenever the gold runs out.

1211
01:18:25,499 --> 01:18:26,693
早点回来！
Come back soon!

1212
01:18:26,834 --> 01:18:31,862
妈妈，让他们多玩会吧 反正纽约又不会跑，是不是，伙计们？
Mom, let them take their time. New York isn't going anywhere, right, guys?

1213
01:18:31,939 --> 01:18:33,964
说的没错！
You're right about that!

1214
01:18:34,041 --> 01:18:35,975
只要我能和她在一起…
As long as I'm with her...

1215
01:18:36,043 --> 01:18:39,843
…在哪都是天堂
...and you two, I don't care where we are.

1216
01:18:40,114 --> 01:18:42,605
她笑起来真美
She has the most amazing laugh.

1217
01:18:45,452 --> 01:18:47,784
爱果然是没界限啊！
Love has no boundaries!

1218
01:18:48,722 --> 01:18:51,054
看来你得忍受我们一段时间了
Looks like you're stuck with us for a while.

1219
01:18:54,128 --> 01:18:56,562
爸爸？怎么了？
Dad? What's wrong?

1220
01:18:56,630 --> 01:18:59,292
我只是觉得我们可以…
I just thought we could hang out a bit and...

1221
01:19:01,735 --> 01:19:03,862
- 你骗到我了！ - 我骗到你了，儿子！
- You got me! - I got you, son!

1222
01:19:04,138 --> 01:19:07,539
我的招数都被你学去了
You got me with my thing. You brought it back around on me.

1223
01:19:10,477 --> 01:19:12,138
我骗到你了！
I got you, son!

1224
01:19:12,746 --> 01:19:15,078
老爹还不赖吧，是不是，马蒂？
The old man's not too bad, eh, Marty?

1225
01:19:15,149 --> 01:19:17,583
- 马蒂？谁是马蒂？ - 少来了
- Marty? Who's Marty? - Come on.

1226
01:19:17,651 --> 01:19:20,916
- 我不知道谁是马蒂 - 你骗不了我
- I don't know no Marty. - You can't fool me.

1227
01:19:20,988 --> 01:19:23,183
这儿没马蒂啊
Ain't no Marty here.

1228
01:19:23,257 --> 01:19:27,694
马蒂！我看你眼睛就知道是你啦
Marty! I can look into your eyes, and I know it's you.

1229
01:19:27,761 --> 01:19:31,026
<i>我一直在流浪 永远在流浪
See, I've been traveling Been traveling forever</i>

1230
01:19:31,098 --> 01:19:34,363
<i>现在找到一个家 像是在天堂徜徉
But now that I found a home feels like I'm in heaven</i>

1231
01:19:34,434 --> 01:19:37,699
<i>我一直在流浪 永远在流浪
See, I've been traveling Been traveling forever</i>

1232
01:19:37,771 --> 01:19:39,602
<i>现在找到一个家
But now that I'm home</i>

1233
